\id 2CH - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020
\h 2 Weche Mag Ndalo
\toc1 Weche Mag Ndalo Mar Ariyo
\toc2 2 Weche Mag Ndalo
\toc3 2We
\mt1 Weche Mag Ndalo Mar Ariyo
\c 1
\s1 Solomon okwayo rieko
\p 
\v 1 Solomon wuod Daudi nogurore motegno e pinye nikech Jehova Nyasaye Nyasache ne ni kode kendo ne okete obedo ngʼama duongʼ miwuoro.
\p 
\v 2 Eka Solomon nowuoyo gi jo-Israel duto, magin jotend migepe mag jolweny alufu achiel kod jotend jolweny mag mia achiel, gi jongʼad bura, to gi jotelo duto man Israel, kaka jotend dhoudi.
\v 3 Kendo Solomon gi chokruok duto nodhi kar lemo motingʼore malo e Gibeon nikech Hemb Romo mar Nyasaye mane Musa jatich Jehova Nyasaye noloso e thim ne ni kanyo.
\v 4 Noyudo ka Daudi nosekelo Sandug Nyasaye koa Kiriath Jearim nyaka kama noselosone, nikech nosegurone hema Jerusalem.
\v 5 To kendo mar misango mar mula mane Bezalel wuod Uri ma wuod Hur noloso ne ni Gibeon e nyim hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, omiyo Solomon kod oganda duto nolamo Nyasaye kanyo.
\v 6 Solomon noidho malo kar kendo mar misango mar mula e nyim Jehova Nyasaye ei Hemb Romo, mochiwo misengini miwangʼo pep alufu achiel.
\p 
\v 7 Gotieno nogo Nyasaye nofwenyore ne Solomon mowachone niya, “Kwa gimoro amora midwaro mondo amiyi.”
\p 
\v 8 Solomon nodwoko Nyasaye niya, “isenyiso ngʼwono maduongʼ ni Daudi wuora kendo iketa abedo ruoth kare.
\v 9 Koro, Jehova Nyasaye, mad imi singruok mane imiyo wuora Daudi ochopi, nikech iseketa ruoth kuom oganda mangʼeny ka buru manie piny.
\v 10 Miya rieko kod ngʼeyo mondo atel ne ogandani nimar en ngʼa manyalo telo ni oganda maduongʼ machalo kama?”
\p 
\v 11 Nyasaye nodwoko Solomon niya, “Nikech ma e gima chunyi dwaro kendo ne ok ikwaya mwandu kata duongʼ kata pak, kata tho mar wasiki, kata kwayo mondo idag amingʼa, to isekwayo rieko kod ngʼeyo kaka dirit ogandana ma aseketi ibedo e ruoth,
\v 12 omiyo anamiyi rieko kod ngʼeyo. Kendo abiro miyi mwandu kod duongʼ kod pak maonge ruoth kata achiel kuom mago moteloni kata mabiro bangʼi nobedgo.”
\p 
\v 13 Bangʼe Solomon nodok Jerusalem koa kamotingʼore gi malo man Gibeon, e nyim Hemb Romo. Kendo notiyo tich ruoth Israel.
\p 
\v 14 Solomon nongʼiewo geche mag lweny kod farese; ne en gi geche lweny alufu achiel mia angʼwen kod farese alufu apar gariyo mane oketo e mier madongo mag geche lweny to moko bende noketo Jerusalem kama nodake.
\v 15 Ruoth nomiyo fedha gi dhahabu obedo manwangʼo yot ka kidi akida Jerusalem kendo yiend sida ne ngʼeny mana ka yiend ngʼowu ma otwi e got.
\v 16 Solomon nokelo farese koa Misri kod e piny miluongo ni Kue, johala mag ruoth nongʼiewogi e piny Kue.
\v 17 Negingʼiewo gach lweny koa Misri e nengo mar kilo abiriyo mar fedha kendo faras achiel e nengo maromo kilo ariyo. Bende ne giusogi ni ruodhi duto mag jo-Hiti gi jo-Aram.
\c 2
\s1 Chenro mar gero hekalu
\p 
\v 1 Solomon nochiwo chik mondo ger hekalu ni Nying Jehova Nyasaye kod ode mar ruoth.
\v 2 Nondiko jotingʼ gik moko ji alufu piero abiriyo (70,000) gi jopa kite e got ji alufu piero aboro (80,000) kod nyipeche alufu adek gi mia auchiel (3,600).
\p 
\v 3 Solomon noorone Hiram ruodh Turo wach niya,
\pm “Orna yiend sida kaka ne iorone wuora Daudi sida mane ogerogo ode mar dak.
\v 4 Sani achiegni gero hekalu ni Nying Jehova Nyasaye Nyasacha mondo achiwne kaka kar wangʼo ubani mangʼwe ngʼar e nyime. Hekaluni nobed kama iketoe makati mowal e nyime pile, kendo kama ichiwoe misengini miwangʼo pep mapile pile okinyi godhiambo. Misenginigi bende notim kinde Sabato kod ndalo ma dwe opor, kaachiel gi sewni moyier mag Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa. Ma en chik mochwere ni jo-Israel.
\pm 
\v 5 “Hekalu ma anager nobed maduongʼ nikech Nyasachwa duongʼ moloyo nyiseche mamoko duto.
\v 6 To en ngʼa manyalo gerone hekalu, ka kata polo malo kata polo mabor moloyo ok nyal romi? An to an ngʼa mondo agerne hekalu makmana gero kama iwangʼoe misengini e nyime?
\pm 
\v 7 “Yie iorna ngʼama olony e tij dhahabu kod fedha, kod mula kod nyinyo kendo mongʼeyo loso law maralik gi makwar kod marambulu kendo man-gi ngʼeyo kuom goro gik mamoko mondo oti gi jotichna molony man Juda gi Jerusalem mane Daudi wuora oketo.
\pm 
\v 8 “Kowna bende yiend sida gi saipras gi algumo mag Lebanon nimar angʼeyo ni jotiji olony e ngʼado yiende kanyo. Jotijena biro tiyo kanyakla kod jotijegi
\v 9 mondo giikna yiende mangʼeny nikech hekalu magero nyaka bed maduongʼ kendo miwuoro.
\v 10 Anami jotichni ma jongʼad yien gunde alufu piero angʼwen (40,000) mag ngano moregi, gi gunde alufu piero ariyo gariyo (20,000) mag shairi gi degi alufu angʼwen (4,000) mag divai kod depe alufu angʼwen (4,000) mag mo.”
\p 
\v 11 Hiram ruodh Turo nodwoko Solomon gi baruwa kowacho:
\pm “Nikech Jehova Nyasaye ohero joge oseketi idoko ruodhgi.”
\p 
\v 12 Kendo Hiram nomedo wacho niya,
\pm “Pak odogne Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach jo-Israel mane ochweyo polo gi piny! Osemiyo Ruoth Daudi wuowi mariek, mongʼeyo fwono tiend weche kendo fwenyo gik moko, en ema noger hekalu ne Jehova Nyasaye to gi od ruoth modakie owuon.
\pm 
\v 13 “Aoroni Huram-Abi ngʼat man-gi lony maduongʼ
\v 14 ma min-gi ne nyar Dan to wuon-gi ne ja-Turo. Ne otiegore e tije dhahabu, kod fedha, mula kod nyinyo, kidi kod yien, kendo kuom loso lewni maralik gi marambulu gi marakwaro to gi law katana maber. En kod lony mangʼeny kuom kit goro duto kendo loso kido moro amora momiye. Enoti gi jotijegi molony kaachiel gi mag ruodha Daudi wuonu.
\pm 
\v 15 “Emomiyo ruodha yie iorna ngano gi shairi kod mo zeituni kod divai mane isingo.
\v 16 Wanatongʼ yiend Lebanon moromo kaka idwaro kendo nwatwegi kanyakla ma wakwangʼ-gi e nam nyaka Jopa, eka iniomgi mitergi Jerusalem.”
\p 
\v 17 Solomon nokwano jodak duto man Israel bangʼ kwan mane wuon mare Daudi nosekwano kendo noyudo ni gin ji alufu mia achiel gi piero abich gadek gi mia auchiel (153,600).
\v 18 Ne oketo ji alufu piero abiriyo (70,000) kuomgi mondo obed jotingʼo to ji alufu piero aboro (80,000) opa kite e gode kaachiel gi ji alufu adek gi mia auchiel (3,600) ma nyipechegi mondo omi ji oti.
\c 3
\s1 Solomon ogero hekalu
\p 
\v 1 Bangʼe Solomon nochako gero hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye Jerusalem e got Moria kama Jehova Nyasaye nofwenyore ne Daudi wuon mare. Ne en e kar dino cham mar Arauna ja-Jebus kama Daudi nochiwo.
\v 2 Nochako gedo odiechiengʼ mar ariyo e dwe mar ariyo e higa mar angʼwen mar lochne.
\p 
\v 3 Mise mar gero hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye mane Solomon oketo ne en kama: borne ne romo fut piero aboro gaboro gi nus, lachne ne romo fut piero ariyo gochiko gi nus kaluwore gi rapim machon.
\v 4 Bor mar agola mane ni e nyim hekalu ne romo fut piero ariyo gochiko gi nus maromre gi lach mar hekalu kendo borne modhi malo ne romo fut piero ariyo gochiko gi nus.
\p Nobawo iye gi dhahabu maler.
\v 5 Nochwado i hekalu kod yiend saipras kendo ne omuone kod dhahabu maler moketogi gi othidhe kod thiwni.
\v 6 Nolicho hekalu gi kite ma nengogi tek, kendo notiyo kod dhahabu mogol Parvaim.
\v 7 Nobawo hekalu gi dhahabu koda ka sirni, gi Sirni mag dhoudi gi yiend tado, kor udi gi dhoudi, kendo nogoro malaika mar kerubi e kor udi.
\p 
\v 8 Ne ogero Kama Ler Moloyo kendo borne ne romo gi lach hekalu, borne gi lachne ne en fut piero ariyo gochiko gi nus. Ne omuono iye gi dhahabu maler ma pekne romo kilo alufu piero ariyo.
\v 9 Pek dhahabu mar musmal mane otiyogo ne romo nus kilo. Nobawo udi mamalo bende gi dhahabu.
\p 
\v 10 E Kama Ler Moloyo nopayo kerubi ariyo kendo obawogi kod dhahabu.
\v 11 Bor mar bwomb kerubi ne en mita ochiko. Bwomb kerubi achiel ne romo fut aboro kendo nomulo kor hekalu to eka bwombe machielo ma borne bende ne fut aboro nomulo bwomb kerubi machielo.
\v 12 Machalre bende, bwomb kerubi achiel machielo borne ne romo fut aboro kendo nomulo bath hekalu komachielo, to bwombe machielo ma bende borne ne romo fut aboro nomulo bwomb kerubi mokwongo.
\v 13 Bwomb kerubigo noyarore maromo fut piero ariyo gochiko gi nus. Kerubigo nochungʼ ka ngʼiyo dir ot maduongʼ.
\p 
\v 14 Noloso pasia mar nanga marambulu, gi maralik, gi makwar kod law mayom motwangʼe kido mar kerubi.
\p 
\v 15 E nyim hekalu noloso sirni ariyo ma borgi ne romo fut piero abich gariyo gi nus koriw kendo noum wi moro ka moro gi gima borne romo fut aboro.
\v 16 Noloso thiwni kendo oketogi ewi sirnigo. Bende noloso gik mongʼinore ongʼinore mia achiel mag mula kendo nolierogi e thiwnigo.
\v 17 Nochungo sirnigo e nyim hekalu koketo achiel yo milambo to machielo yo nyandwat. Mane oketo yo milambo noluongo ni Jakin to manoketo nyandwat noluongo ni Boaz.
\c 4
\s1 Gige hekalu
\p 
\v 1 Noloso kendo mar misango mar mula ma borne gi lachne romo fut piero ariyo gochiko gi nus, to borne modhi malo romo fut apar gabich.
\v 2 Eka noloso Nam mar mula moleny, molworore kaka karaya ma lachne romo fut apar gabich, to tutne romo fut aboro. Alworane duto ne romo fut piero angʼwen gangʼwen.
\v 3 E bwo dhoge, nolwore gi kido apar mokedi mag rwedhi maromo fut achiel gi nus. Rwedhigo nolos koriedo e laini ariyo ka gimakore gi Namno.
\p 
\v 4 Karaya mar Namno norenji e ngʼe rwedhi apar gariyo, ka adek ngʼiyo yo nyandwat, to adek ngʼiyo yo podho chiengʼ, to adek ngʼiyo yo milambo, bende adek ngʼiyo yo wuok chiengʼ. Karaya mar Namno noyiere kuomgi kendo tiendegi machien nochomo ka iye.
\v 5 Lachne ne romo bat achiel morie, to dhoge ne chalo gi dho kikombe mana ka ondanyo mathiewo. To notingʼo pi manyalo romo lita alufu piero auchiel gauchiel.
\p 
\v 6 Bangʼe noloso kareche apar mag luoko kendo noketo abich yo milambo to abich yo nyandwat. Karechego ema ne ilwokoe gik mane itiyogo kuom misengini miwangʼo pep to Karaya Maduongʼ to ne jodolo lwokoree.
\p 
\v 7 Ne oloso gig teche mag dhahabu kaluwore gi kaka nochike kuom losogi kendo noketogi e hekalu ka abich oket yo milambo, to abich yo nyandwat.
\p 
\v 8 Noloso mesni apar moketogi e hekalu, ka abich oket yo milambo to abich yo nyandwat. Bende noloso tewni mia achiel mag dhahabu mikirogo.
\p 
\v 9 Noloso laru mar jodolo kod laru maduongʼ gi dhout laru kendo nobawo dhoudigo gi mula.
\v 10 Ne oketo Karaya Maduongʼ e bathe ma yo milambo momanyo kind yo wuok chiengʼ kod milambo.
\p 
\v 11 Bende noloso agulni gi opewni kod tewni mag kiro remo.
\p Kamano Huram notieko tich duto mane otimo ne Ruoth Solomon e hekalu mar Nyasaye. Ne gin:
\b
\li1 
\v 12 Sirni ariyo,
\li1 agulni ariyo machalo tawo moketi ewi sirni;
\li1 thiwni ariyo mane okedgo gik machalo tawo moketi ewi sirni;
\li1 
\v 13 gik mongʼinore mia angʼwen mag thiwni ariyo moluwore (laini ariyo mag thiwni oketi e laini ariyo mag gik mongʼinore mane okedgo gik machalo agulni molos kaka tawo ewi sirni);
\li1 
\v 14 bende noloso rachungi gi karechegi;
\li1 
\v 15 Karaya mar Nam gi rwedhi apar gariyo manie e bwoye;
\li1 
\v 16 agulni gi opewni kod ojiko mar uma michwoyogo ringʼo to gi gik mamoko matiyo kodgi.
\b
\p Huram-Abi noloso ne Ruoth Solomon gik moko duto mag hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye gi mula mopwodhi.
\v 17 Ruoth nomiyo giwangʼo lowo mane gisechweyo e paw Jordan man e kind Sukoth gi Zarethan.
\v 18 Gigi duto mane Solomon oloso duto ne ngʼeny omiyo kata pek mula mane olosgo gigo ne ok nyal ngʼere.
\p 
\v 19 Kendo Solomon noloso gik moko duto mane nitie e hekalu mar Nyasaye kaka:
\b
\li1 kendo mar misango mar dhahabu,
\li1 mesni mag makati miketo e Nyim Nyasaye pile,
\li1 
\v 20 rachungi teyni molos gi dhahabu maler kaachiel gi techegi monego liel e nyim kama ler mar lemo kaka nondiki;
\li1 
\v 21 kod maupe mag dhahabu gi teyni kod ramekni (ne gin dhahabu duto);
\li1 
\v 22 kod gima ingʼadogo otambi mar teyni molos gi dhahabu maler, gi tewni mag kiro remo, gi dise gi tawo mar ubani kod dhout hekalu mar dhahabu: dhoudi mar ot maiye gi Kama Ler Moloyo kaachiel gi dhoudi mag dier ot maduongʼ.
\b
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Ka tije duto mane Solomon osetimo e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye noserumo, nokelo gik duto mane Daudi wuon-gi osewalo kaka fedha gi dhahabu kod gik mitimogo lemo kendo noketogi e od keno mar hekalu mar Nyasaye.
\s1 Sandug Muma okel e hekalu
\p 
\v 2 Bangʼe Solomon noluongo jodong jo-Israel, jodong dhoudi duto gi jotend anywola mag Israel mondo odhi ire Jerusalem mondo gikel Sandug Muma mar singruok mar Jehova Nyasaye koa e Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi miluongo ni Sayun.
\v 3 Jo-Israel duto nobiro kanyakla ir ruoth e ndalo Sawo matimore dwe mar abiriyo.
\p 
\v 4 Kane jodong Israel duto osechopo jo-Lawi nokawo Sandug Muma,
\v 5 kendo negikelo Sandug Muma gi Hemb Romo kod gik moko duto maler manie iye. Jodolo mane jo-Lawi notingʼogi;
\v 6 kendo Ruoth Solomon kod oganda jo-Israel duto mane ochokore molwore nochopo e nyim Sandug Muma; kendo negichiwo rombe kod dhok mangʼeny mane kwan-gi ok nyal ndiki kata kwan kaka misango.
\p 
\v 7 Eka jodolo nokelo Sandug Muma mar singruok mar Jehova Nyasaye kama ne olosne ei kama ler mar lemo mar hekalu, ma en Kama Ler Moloyo mi gikete e bwomb kerubi.
\v 8 Kerubigo noyaro bwombegi ewi kama noketie Sandug Muma gi ludhe mitingʼego.
\v 9 Ludhegi ne boyo ahinya kochakore e Sandug Muma ma gikogi ne inyalo ne koa e nyim kama ler mar lemo, to ne ok ginen gi oko mar Kama Ler kendo pod gin kanyo nyaka chil kawuono.
\v 10 Ne onge gimoro ei Sandug Muma makmana kite ariyo mopa mane Musa oketo e iye kane en Horeb kama Jehova Nyasaye ne otimoe singruok kod jo-Israel kane gisewuok Misri.
\p 
\v 11 Bangʼe jodolo bangʼe nowuok oa Kama Ler. Jodolo duto mane ni kanyo nopwodhore ka ok odewo ni gin e migepe mage mag tich.
\v 12 Jo-Lawi duto mane jothum kaka Asaf, Heman, Jeduthun kod yawuotgi gi jowetene nochungʼ e bath kendo mar misango yo wuok chiengʼ ka girwako lewni mar katana maber ka gigoyo ongengʼo gi nyatiti kod orutu. Jodolo mia achiel gi piero ariyo to ne goyo turumbete.
\v 13 Jogo turumbete kaachiel gi jower ne wer gi chuny achiel ka gima ne en dwond ngʼato achiel ka gipako kendo goyone Jehova Nyasaye erokamano. Kaachiel ka gigoyo turumbete gi ongengʼo to gi thumbe mamoko negitingʼo dwondgi malo ka gipako Jehova Nyasaye kendo ka giwer niya,
\q1 “Jehova Nyasaye ber;
\q2 kendo herane osiko manyaka chiengʼ.”
\p Eka hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye nopongʼ kod bor polo,
\v 14 kendo jodolo ne ok nyal tiyo tijegi nikech bor polo, nimar duongʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye nopongʼo hekalu mar Nyasaye.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Eka Solomon nowacho niya, “Jehova Nyasaye osewacho ni enodag ei bor polo motimo mudho.
\v 2 Asegeroni hekalu marahuma, kama inidagie nyaka chiengʼ.”
\p 
\v 3 Kane oganda jo-Israel duto ochungʼ kanyo, ruoth nolokore mogwedhogi.
\v 4 Eka nowacho niya,
\pm “Pak obed ne Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel, mosetimo gi lwete gima ne osingo gi dhoge ni Daudi wuonwa. Nikech nowacho niya,
\v 5 ‘Chakre ndalo mane agolo joga koa Misri pok ayiero dala maduongʼ e dhoot moro amora mar Israel mondo oger hekalu kanyo ni Nyinga, to aseyiero Daudi mondo otel ni joga Israel.
\v 6 To koro aseyiero Jerusalem mondo obed kama Nyinga betie kendo aseyiero Daudi mondo otel ni joga Israel.’
\pm 
\v 7 “Daudi wuora noketo e chunye mondo oger hekalu moluongo nying Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel.
\v 8 To Jehova Nyasaye nowacho ni Daudi wuora niya, ‘Nitimo maber mondo ibed gi wach gero hekalu ni nyinga e chunyi.
\v 9 Kata kamano in ok niger hekalu, to wuodi, ma en ringri gi rembi iwuon; en ema noger hekalu ni Nyinga.’
\pm 
\v 10 “Jehova Nyasaye oserito singruok mane otimo. Asekawo loch wuora Daudi kendo asebet e kom loch mar Israel mana kaka Nyasaye nosingo kendo asegero hekalu ni Nying Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel.
\v 11 Aseketo Sandug Muma ma moketie singruok mane Jehova Nyasaye otimo e kinde gi jo-Israel.”
\s1 Lemb Solomon mar Walo hekalu
\p 
\v 12 Eka Solomon nochungʼ e nyim kendo mar misango mar Jehova Nyasaye e nyim oganda duto mar jo-Israel kendo norieyo bedene kochomo malo.
\v 13 Noseloso raidhi mar mula ma borne gi lachne romo fut aboro to borne kadhi malo en fut abich mokete e dier laru ma oko. Ne ochungʼ e raidhino mi ogoyo chonge piny e nyim oganda duto mar jo-Israel kendo norieyo bedene kochomo polo.
\v 14 Kowacho niya,
\pm “Yaye Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel, onge Nyasaye moro e polo kata e piny machal kodi. In e Nyasaye marito singruok mar herane ni jotichne maluwo yoreni gi chunygi duto.
\v 15 Iserito singruokni mane itimo gi jatichni Daudi wuora, ne isingori gi dhogi kendo isechopo singruokno gi lweti, mana kaka en kawuononi.
\pm 
\v 16 “To koro Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel rit singruok mane itimo gi jatichni Daudi wuora kiwachone niya, ‘Ok inibed maonge ngʼama bet e nyima e kom loch Israel ka nyikwayi onono kaka giwuotho e nyima kaka chikna dwaro mana kaka isetimo.’
\v 17 To koro, yaye Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel yie mondo wach mane isingo ni jatichni Daudi wuora otimre mana kaka ne isingo.
\pm 
\v 18 “To bende Nyasaye nyalo dak e piny kod ji? Kata polo malo kata polo mabor ok nyal romi, to koro hekalu mageroni to diromi nade!
\v 19 Kata kamano chik iti ni lamo jatichni gi kwayone mar ngʼwono yaye Jehova Nyasaye Nyasacha. Winji ywak gi lemo ma jatichni lamo e nyimi.
\v 20 Mad wangʼi rang hekaluni odiechiengʼ kod otieno, kama niwacho ni Nyingi nobedie. Yie iwinji lemo ma jatichni lamo kochomo odni.
\v 21 Winji lamo mar jatichni kaachiel gi jogi Israel ka gilamo ka gichomo odni. Winji gi e polo kar dakni kendo kiwinjo to iwenwa richowa.
\pm 
\v 22 “Ka ngʼato oketho ni wadgi kendo dwarore ni mondo okwongʼre kendo obiro mokwongʼore e nyim kendo mar misango manie hekaluni,
\v 23 to iwinji gi e polo kendo itim kaka owinjore. Ngʼad bura e kind jotichni kikumo joketho kendo iket richogi e wigi bende joma onge ketho iket kare kaluwore gi timgi makare.
\pm 
\v 24 “Ka jogi Israel olo e lweny gi jowasikgi nikech gisekethoni to bangʼe gilokore mi gipako nyingi, ka gilamo kendo gikwayo e hekaluni,
\v 25 to iwinjgi gi e polo kendo iwe richo jogi Israel kendo iduog-gi e piny mane imiyogi kod kweregi.
\pm 
\v 26 “Ka polo olor kendo koth onge nikech jogi osekethoni to ka gilemo kaeni ka gipako nyingi kendo ka gilokore giweyo richogi nikech isekelonegi chandruok,
\v 27 to yie mondo iwinjgi gie polo kendo iwene jotichni ma jo-Israel richogi. Puonjgi yo makare mar dak kendo iornegi koth e piny mane imiyo jogi kaka girkeni margi.
\pm 
\v 28 “Ka kech kata dera omako piny kata ka abach omako cham kata tuo ewi dongo, kata ka bonyo kata kungu, kata ka jowasigu olworo miechgi madongo, kata ka midekre kata tuo omakogi,
\v 29 to ka ngʼato kuom jogi ma jo-Israel olemo kata okwayi, ka gingʼeyo gima chando chunygi kod lit ka girieyo bedegi kochomo hekaluni,
\v 30 to yie iwinji gie polo kama idakie. Wenegi richogi kendo tim ne ngʼato ka ngʼato gima owinjore gi gik motimo nikech ingʼeyo chunygi (nikech in kendi ema ingʼeyo chuny dhano),
\v 31 mondo omi gilwori kendo giwuoth e yoreni ndalogi duto ma gin-go e piny mane imiyo kwerewa.
\pm 
\v 32 “To kuom jadak ma ok achiel kuom jogi Israel moa e piny mabor nikech nyingi maduongʼ kendo lweti maratego kod badi marabora moriere, ka gibiro ma gilemo ka gichomo hekaluni,
\v 33 to yie mondo iwinji gie polo kama idakie kendo tim gimoro amora ma jadakno okwayi mondo ogendini duto mag piny ongʼe nyingi kendo oluori mana kaka jogi Israel kendo mondo gingʼe ni ot ma asegeroni luongo nyingi.
\pm 
\v 34 “Ka jogi odhi kedo gi jowasikgi kamoro amora ma ibiro orogie ka gilami kagichomo dalani miseyiero kendo hekalu masegero maluongo nyingi,
\v 35 to yie iwinji gie polo lamogi kod kwayogi kendo konygi.
\pm 
\v 36 “To ka giketho e nyimi, nimar onge ngʼato kata achiel ma ok jaketho mi ikecho kodgi kendo ichiwogi e lwet wasigu mi giterogi e twech e piny mabor kata machiegni,
\v 37 kendo ka chunygi olokore e piny mane otergi e twech kendo giweyo richogi kendo gikwayi e piny wasikgi mane otweyogi kagiwacho niya, ‘Wasetimo richo kendo waseketho bende wasetimo mamono;’
\v 38 to ka gidwogo iri gi chunygi duto kod ngimagi duto e piny mane otergi e twech, kendo gilemo ka girango pinygi mane imiyo kweregi, kod dala maduongʼ miseyiero kod hekalu ma asegero ni nyingi,
\v 39 to yie iwinji lemogi gi kwayogi gie polo kar dakni kendo ikonygi. Kendo iwe ni jogi mosetimo richo e nyimi.
\pm 
\v 40 “Koro Nyasacha, yie mondo wengegi oyawre kendo itgi mondo owinj maber lemo ma wachiwo kaeni.
\qm1 
\v 41 “Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, koro chungʼ malo kendo idonj e kar yweyo,
\qm2 in kaachiel gi Sandug Muma mar singruokni mar tekoni maduongʼ.
\qm1 Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, mad jodolo magi orwakre gi warruok,
\qm2 mad jogi maler obed gi ilo kuom berni.
\qm1 
\v 42 Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, kik ikwed ngʼatno misewiro.
\qm2 Par hera maduongʼ mane isingone Daudi jatichni.”
\c 7
\s1 Walo hekalu
\p 
\v 1 Kane Solomon otieko lemo, mach nolwar koa e polo mowangʼo misango miwangʼo pep kod misengini mamoko kendo duongʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye nopongʼo hekalu.
\v 2 Jodolo ne ok nyal donjo e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye nikech duongʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye nopongʼe.
\v 3 Kane jo-Israel duto noneno mach koa e polo kabiro piny kod duongʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye kani ewi hekalu negigoyo chongegi e ndiri ka gikulore auma. Negilamo kendo goyone Jehova Nyasaye erokamano, kagiwacho niya,
\q1 “Jehova Nyasaye ber
\q2 kendo herane osiko manyaka chiengʼ.”
\m 
\v 4 Eka ruoth kod ji duto nochiwo misengini e nyim Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 5 Ruoth Solomon nochiwo misango gi dhok alufu piero ariyo gi ariyo kod rombe gi diek maromo alufu mia achiel gi piero ariyo. Kamano ruoth kod ji duto nowalo hekalu mar Nyasaye.
\v 6 Jodolo nokawo keregi kaachiel gi jo-Lawi ka goyo thumbe mag Jehova Nyasaye mane ruoth Daudi nolosone pako Jehova Nyasaye kendo mane itiyogo kane odwoko erokamano kowacho niya, “Herane osiko manyaka chiengʼ.” Jodolo mane ochungʼ momanyore gi jo-Lawi ne goyo turumbete ka jo-Israel duto nochungʼ.
\p 
\v 7 Solomon nopwodho dier laru mane nitie e nyim hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kendo kanyo nochiwoe misengini miwangʼo pep kod boche miwangʼo mag misango mar lalruok nikech kendo mar misango mar mula manoloso ne ok nyal tingʼo misengini miwangʼo, gi chiwo mag cham kod boche.
\p 
\v 8 E ndalogo Solomon kod jo-Israel duto notimo sawo kuom ndalo abiriyo. Ne en chokruok maduongʼ mochakore Lebo Hamath nyaka Wadi man Misri.
\v 9 Chiengʼ mar aboro negichokore nikech negisepwodho kendo mar misango kuom ndalo abiriyo kendo sawo bende kuom ndalo abiriyo.
\v 10 To odiechiengʼ mar piero ariyo gadek mar dwe mar abiriyo nomiyo ji thuolo mondo odog e miechgi ka gimor gi ilo e chunygi nikech gik mabeyo mane Jehova Nyasaye osetimo ni Daudi gi Solomon kendo ni joge Israel.
\s1 Jehova Nyasaye ofwenyore ne Solomon
\p 
\v 11 Kane Solomon osetieko gero hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kod od ruoth mar dak kendo nosetieko timo gik moko duto manochano mondo otim e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kod ode owuon;
\v 12 Jehova Nyasaye nofwenyorene gotieno mowacho niya,
\pm “Asewinjo lemoni kendo aseyiero hekalu ka kaka kara mitimoe misengini.
\pm 
\v 13 “Ka aloro polo ni koth kik chuwe kata ka keto bonyo mondo ocham piny kata aoro dera marach mar tho ne joga,
\v 14 to ka joga miluongo gi nyinga obolore ka lemo kendo manyo wangʼa, ka giweyo yoregi maricho, eka nawinj gie polo, mi nawenegi richogi kendo nares pinygi.
\v 15 Eka nangʼigi kendo nachik ita ni lemo molam ka.
\v 16 Aseyiero kendo pwodho hekaluni mondo nyinga obedie nyaka chiengʼ, wengena kod chunya nobed kanyo kinde duto.
\pm 
\v 17 “To in kiwuotho e nyima kaka Daudi wuonu notimo kendo itimo duto ma achiko kendo rito chikena gi buchena,
\v 18 eka anagur lochni mar ruoth kaka ne asingorane Daudi wuonu, kane awachone ni, ‘Ok inibed maonge ngʼato marito jo-Israel kaka ruoth.’
\pm 
\v 19 “To kulokoru mi ok umako wechena kod chikena ma asemiyou kendo udhi mondo uti ne nyiseche mamoko kendo lamogi,
\v 20 napudh jo-Israel oko ma agolgi e pinya mane amiyogi kendo anakwed hekaluni ma asepwodho nikech Nyinga. Enobed ka ngero kendo gima ji duto jaro.
\v 21 Kata obedo ni hekaluni koro nigi duongʼ, ji duto mabiro kadho bute nowuor kendo nohum ka gipenjo ni, ‘Angʼo momiyo Jehova Nyasaye osetimo gima chalo kama ni pinyni kod hekaluni?’
\v 22 Ji nodwokgi ni, ‘Nikech negiweyo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kweregi manogologi e piny Misri mine gikawo nyiseche mamoko ka gilamogi kendo tiyonegi ma emomiyo osekelo masichegi duto kuomgi.’ ”
\c 8
\s1 Gik mamoko mane Solomon otimo
\p 
\v 1 E giko higni piero ariyo mane Solomon ogerogo hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kod kare owuon mar dak,
\v 2 Solomon noloso mier matindo mane Hiram omiye kendo noketoe jo-Israel mondo odagie.
\v 3 Bangʼe Solomon nodhi Hamath Zoba mokawe.
\v 4 Bende nogero Tadmor mane nitie e thim kaachiel gi mier madongo mag keno manogero Hamath.
\v 5 Noloso Beth Horon Mamalo kod Beth Horon Mamwalo kaka mier madongo mochiel gohinga motegno kendo oketnegi rangeye miloro gi lodi.
\v 6 Bende nogero Baalath kaachiel gi mier duto madongo mag keno kod mier duto madongo mag geche lweny to gi faresegi, Solomon nogero gimoro amora mane odwaro gero Jerusalem gi Lebanon kod gwenge duto mane nitie e bwo lochne.
\p 
\v 7 Ji duto mane odongʼ e pinyno koa kuom jo-Hiti, gi jo-Amor kod jo-Perizi, gi jo-Hivi kod jo-Jebus (ogendinigi ne ok jo-Israel),
\v 8 tiende ni, nyikwagi mane odongʼ e piny ma jo-Israel ne ok otieko, Solomon nolokogi wasumbini michuno mondo oti githuon, kaka obet nyaka chil kawuono,
\v 9 To Solomon ne ok oloko jo-Israel wasumbini kuom tije, to noketogi kaka jolwenje, jotelo mag jotend lweny kod jotelo mag geche lweny kod joriemb gechene.
\v 10 Bende ne gin jodong Ruoth Solomon madongo ma kar rombgi ne jotelo mia ariyo gi piero abich mane orito ji.
\p 
\v 11 Solomon nogolo nyar Farao e Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi mokelo e od ruoth manogerone kowacho niya, “Chiega ok nyal dak e od ruoth Daudi ma ruodh jo-Israel nikech kuonde ma Sandug Muma mar Jehova Nyasaye mar singruok osedonje gin kuonde maler.”
\p 
\v 12 Solomon nochiwo ne Jehova Nyasaye misengini miwangʼo pep e kendo mar misango mar Jehova Nyasaye mane ogero e nyim agola,
\v 13 kaluwore gi chik mane Musa ogolo kuom chiwo migolo pile ka pile mag odiechienge Sabato, Wuok Dwe, kaachiel gi sewni moyier adek mag higa ka higa ma gin Sawo mar makati ma ok oketie thowi, gi Sawo mar Jumbe kod Sawo mar Kiche.
\v 14 Kaluwore gi chike Daudi wuon mare, Solomon nochano migepe mag jodolo kuom tijegi kendo jo-Lawi notelo ni tich wer kod konyo jodolo kaluwore gi tije mopogore opogore mapile ka pile. Kendo nopogo jorit rangeye gi migepegi kuom rangeye mopogore opogore nikech ma e chik ma Daudi ngʼat Nyasaye nochiko.
\v 15 Kuom weche duto mane ruoth ochiko jodolo kod jo-Lawi ne onge moro amora mane giweyo kata mana weche mag keno.
\p 
\v 16 Tije Solomon duto notim kochakore chiengʼ manochakoe gero hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye nyaka tiekne. Omiyo hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye notiek gero.
\p 
\v 17 Bangʼe Solomon nodhi Ezion Geber kod Elath manie dho nam e piny Edom.
\v 18 Omiyo Hiram nooro yiedhi kikwangʼogi kod jotende owuon, jogo molony kuom tich nam. Jogi kaachiel gi joge Solomon nokwangʼ nyaka Ofir ma gikelo dhahabu ma pekne romo kilo alufu apar gabiriyo kendo negikele ne Ruoth Solomon.
\c 9
\s1 Ruoth madhako mar Sheba odhi limo Solomon
\p 
\v 1 Kane ruoth madhako mar Sheba owinjo humb Solomon, nobiro Jerusalem mondo ruoth oteme gi penj matek. Nobiro gi ji kod gik moko mangʼeny kaka ngamia motingʼo gik mangʼwe ngʼar, dhahabu mangʼeny, kaachiel gi kite ma nengogi tek. Nobiro ir Solomon ma owuoyo kode kuom gima noparo.
\v 2 Solomon nodwoko penjoge duto maonge matek mane ok onyal dwoke.
\v 3 Kane ruoth madhako mar Sheba oneno rieko Solomon kaachiel kod ode mar dak manosegero,
\v 4 gi chiemo mane ni e mesane, gi bet mar jodonge, gi rwakruok mar jotije mapogo chiemo, gi rwakruok mar jotije machiwo divai kod misango miwangʼo pep mane otimo e hekalu Jehova Nyasaye, dhoge nomoko.
\p 
\v 5 Nowachone ruoth niya, “Kare humb timbeni kod riekoni mane awinjo e pinya awuon en adier!
\v 6 To ne ok ayie gi weche mane giwacho nyaka nabiro maneno gi wangʼa awuon. Adier kata nus mar duongʼ riekoni ne ok onyisa; iriek moloyo humbi manyocha awinjo.
\v 7 Mano kaka jogi mor manade! En mor manade ne jotendi mosiko kachungʼ e nyimi kendo winjo riekoni!
\v 8 Pak odogne Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachi mosebedo mamor kodi moketi e kom lochne kaka ruoth mondo itine Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachi. Nikech hera ma Nyasachi oherogo Israel to gi dwarone mondo oritgi nyaka chiengʼ omiyo oseketi ruodhgi mondo ingʼad bura makare.”
\p 
\v 9 Eka nomiyo ruoth dhahabu ma pekne romo kilo alufu angʼwen mia abich, gi gik mangʼeny mangʼwe ngʼar kaachiel gi kite ma nengogi tek. Ne pok obetie gik mangʼeny mangʼwe ngʼar marom gi mago mane Ruoth madhako mar Sheba omiyo Ruoth Solomon.
\p 
\v 10 (Jo-Hiram kod jo-Solomon nokelo dhahabu moa Ofir bende negikelo yiend Algumo kod kite ma nengogi tek.
\v 11 Ruoth notiyo gi yiend Algumo kuom loso raidhi mag hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kaachiel gi ode mar loch bende notiyo kodgi kuom loso nyatiti kod orutu ni jothum. Yien machalo kama ne pod ok one e piny Juda nyaka nene.)
\p 
\v 12 Ruoth Solomon nomiyo ruoth madhako mar Sheba gik moko duto mane chunye dwaro kendo mane okwayo; kendo nomiye gik moko mangʼeny moloyo gik mane okelone. Eka nowuok mi odok e pinye kaachiel gi jotije.
\s1 Duongʼ mane Solomon nigo
\p 
\v 13 Pek dhahabu mane Solomon yudo higa ka higa ne nyalo romo kilo alufu piero ariyo gabich,
\v 14 ka ok okwan mago mag osuch jo-ohala gi johono. To ruodhi mag piny Arabu kod jotend piny bende nokelone Solomon dhahabu kod fedha.
\p 
\v 15 Ruoth Solomon nochwogo kuodi madongo mia ariyo mag dhahabu kendo kuot ka kuot nochwog gi dhahabu ma pekne romo kilo adek gi nus.
\v 16 Bende nochwogo okumbni matindo mia adek mobaw gi dhahabu, okumba ka okumba nobaw gi dhahabu ma pekne romo kilo adek gi nus. Magi duto ruoth noketo e ode manogero e Bungu mag Lebanon.
\p 
\v 17 Eka ruoth noloso kom loch maduongʼ ma iye obaw gi lak liech kendo ngʼeye obaw gi dhahabu mopwodhi.
\v 18 Kom duongʼno ne nigi raidhi mag kuonde minyono auchiel gi raten tielo mar dhahabu mane ochuog kuome. Bethene ariyo ne nigi bede miyienge bat, ka kido mar sibuor molosi ochungʼ e bath moro ka moro.
\v 19 Kido mar sibuoche apar gariyo nochungi e kuonde auchiel minyono kiidho kidhi e kom duongʼ ka moro ka moro ochungi e giko raidh auchiel koni gi koni. Onge pinyruoth moro amora manoseloso kom ruoth machalo kama.
\v 20 Kikombe duto mag Ruoth Solomon nolos gi dhahabu, kod gige ot duto mokonyorego e ode mane ni e Bungu mag Lebanon nolos gi dhahabu mopwodhi. Onge gima nolos gi fedha nikech fedha nokaw ni nengone yot e kinde Solomon.
\v 21 Ruoth ne nigi yiedhi mangʼeny mag ohala mane jo-Hiram kwangʼ-go. Dichiel bangʼ higni adek ka higni adek negidwogo ka gitingʼo dhahabu gi fedha gi leke liech gi ongʼeche kod bimbe.
\p 
\v 22 Ruoth Solomon ne nigi mwandu mangʼeny kod rieko moloyo ruodhi mamoko duto mag piny.
\v 23 Ruodhi duto mag pinje ne biro ir Solomon mondo oyud rieko mane Nyasaye oketo e chunye.
\v 24 Higa ka higa, ngʼato ka ngʼato manobiro nokelo mich kaka gik molos gi fedha kod dhahabu, kandho, gige lweny, gik mangʼwe ngʼar, farese kod punde.
\p 
\v 25 Solomon ne nigi udi alufu angʼwen mag farese kod geche lweny kaachiel gi farese alufu apar gariyo manokano e mier madongo mag geche lweny to moko bende ne en-go Jerusalem.
\v 26 Norito ruodhi manie bwo lochne chakre Aora Yufrate nyaka e piny jo-Filistia nyaka chop e giko tongʼ gi kod Misri.
\v 27 Ruoth nomiyo fedha obedo manwangʼo yot ka kidi akida Jerusalem kendo yiend sida ne ngʼeny mana ka yiend ngʼowu ma otwi e got.
\v 28 Solomon nokelo farese koa Misri kod pinje mamoko duto.
\s1 Tho mar Solomon
\p 
\v 29 Weche moko duto mag loch Solomon, chakruokgi nyaka gikogi, donge ondikgi e kitabu mar Nathan janabi, e kitabu motingʼo weche Ahija ja-Shilo kod e kitap Ido janeno manofwenyorene kuom Jeroboam wuod Nebat?
\v 30 Solomon nobedo ruodh jo-Israel duto ka en Jerusalem kuom higni piero angʼwen.
\v 31 Eka notho moyweyo gi kwerene mi noyike e dala Daudi wuon-gi. Rehoboam wuode nobedo ruoth kare.
\c 10
\s1 Jo-Israel odagi Rehoboam
\p 
\v 1 Rehoboam nodhi Shekem nimar jo-Israel duto nodhi kuno mondo okete ruoth.
\v 2 Kane Jeroboam wuod Nebat nowinjo wachni (ne en Misri kuma noringo odhiye koa kuom Ruoth Solomon), noduogo koa Misri.
\v 3 Omiyo negioro joote ir Jeroboam, mi nobiro ir Rehoboam kaachiel gi jo-Israel duto mi giwachone niya,
\v 4 “Wuonu nomiyowa tingʼ mapek, to koro yie iket tingʼ mapekno kod tij achunano obednwa mayot, to wabiro tiyoni.”
\p 
\v 5 Rehoboam nodwoko niya, “Dhi uduog ira bangʼ ndalo adek.” Bangʼe negia ma gidhi.
\p 
\v 6 Eka Ruoth Rehoboam nonono jodongo manotiyo e bwo wuon-gi Solomon kapod ongima. Nopenjogi niya, “Ere kaka unyalo ngʼadona rieko mondo adwok jogi?”
\p 
\v 7 Negidwoke niya, “Kiyie bedo mangʼwon ne jogi kilombogi kendo kimiyogi dwoko mowinjore, to gibiro bedo jotichni ndalo duto.”
\p 
\v 8 To Rehoboam nodagi rieko mane jodongo ongʼadone kendo nopimo wach gi mbesene mane odongogo kendo ne tiyone.
\v 9 Nopenjogi niya, “Un to uneno nangʼo? Ere kaka dwadwok jogi mawacho ni, ‘Dwok chien tingʼ mapek mane wuonu oketo kuomwa’?”
\p 
\v 10 Mbesene mane odongogo nodwoke niya, “Dwok jogo mosekwayi ni, ‘Wuonu noketo tingʼ mapek kuomwa, yie iket tingʼni obed mayot.’ Koro nyisgi ni, ‘Lith lweta matin duongʼ moloyo nungo wuonwa.
\v 11 Wuonwa noketo kuomu tingʼ mapek; an to abiro medo pekne moloyo. Wuonwa nochwadou gi boka, an to abiro chwadou malit makecho ka thomoni.’ ”
\p 
\v 12 Bangʼ ndalo adek Jeroboam kod oganda duto noduogo ir Rehoboam mana kaka ruoth nosewacho niya, “Dwoguru ira bangʼ ndalo adek.”
\v 13 Ruoth nodwokogi kager. Notamore tiyo gi rieko mane jodongo ongʼadone,
\v 14 moluwo rieko mbesene mowacho niya, “Wuonwa nomiyou tingʼ mapek, an to abiro miyou tingʼ mapek moloyo. Wuonwa nochwadou gi boka, an to abiro chwadou malit ka thomoni makecho.”
\v 15 Omiyo ruoth ne ok odewo kwayo mar ji, nimar Nyasaye ema nomiyo mano otimore mondo ochop wach mane Jehova Nyasaye owacho gi dho Ahija ja-Shilo ne Jeroboam wuod Nebat.
\p 
\v 16 Kane jo-Israel duto noneno ni ruoth nodagi winjo wachgi, negidwoko ruoth niya,
\q1 “Wat mane moriwowa kod Daudi,
\q2 angʼo moriwowa gi wuod Jesse?
\q1 Doguru e hembeu, yaye jo-Israel!
\q2 Rituru dhoutu uwegi, yaye oganda Daudi!”
\m Kuom mano jo-Israel duto nodok e miechgi.
\v 17 To ni jo-Israel mane odak e mier mag Juda, Rehoboam ne pod jatendgi.
\p 
\v 18 Ruoth Rehoboam nooro Adoniram mane jarit joma ichuno mondo oti githuon to jo-Israel duto nochiele gi kite motho. Kata kamano Ruoth Rehoboam nonwangʼo thuolo moidho gache nyaka Jerusalem mondo otony.
\v 19 Kuom mano Israel nongʼanyo ni joka Daudi nyaka chil kawuono.
\c 11
\p 
\v 1 Kane Rehoboam ochopo Jerusalem nochoko dhood Juda gi dhood Benjamin, chwo maromo alufu mia achiel gi piero aboro kendo gidhi giked gi jo-Israel mondo gidwok loch ni Rehoboam.
\p 
\v 2 To wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Shemaya ngʼat Nyasaye niya:
\v 3 “Wachne Rehoboam wuod Solomon ruodh Juda kaachiel gi jo-Israel duto modak Juda kod Benjamin,
\v 4 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye owacho: ‘Kik udhi utug lweny gi oweteu ma jo-Israel. Doguru e miechu ngʼato ka ngʼato, nimar ma osetimore nikech an.’ ” Omiyo negiwinjo wach Jehova Nyasaye mi gidok e miechgi ma ok gidhi kedo kod Jeroboam.
\s1 Rehoboam ochielo Juda motegno
\p 
\v 5 Rehoboam nodak Jerusalem kendo nogero mier masiro Juda ndalo lweny kaka:
\v 6 Bethlehem, Etam, Tekoa,
\v 7 Beth Zur, Soko, Adulam,
\v 8 Gath, Maresha, Zif,
\v 9 Adoraim, Lakish, Azeka,
\v 10 Zora, Aijalon, kod Hebron. Magi ne mier mochiel gohinga motegno e piny Juda kod Benjamin.
\v 11 Nochielogi motegno moketo jotend jolweny kuno kaachiel gi kar kano chiemo, mo zeituni kod divai.
\v 12 Noketo okumbini kod tonge e miechgi duto kendo nomiyo gibedo motegno. Kuom mano jo-Juda kod jo-Benjamin ne joge.
\p 
\v 13 Jodolo kaachiel gi jo-Lawi manodak kuonde mopogore opogore mag jo-Israel noriwe lwedo.
\v 14 Jo-Lawi nojwangʼo kuondegi mag kweth kod mwandugi kendo negibiro Juda kod Jerusalem nikech Jeroboam gi yawuote noriembogi e tich kaka jodolo mag Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 15 Noyiero jodolo mage mag kuonde motingʼore kendo mondo odolne nyiseche manono manoloso e kit diel gi nyaroya.
\v 16 Jogo manoa e dhout jo-Israel mane oketo chunygi kuom dwaro Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach jo-Israel, noluoro jo-Lawi nyaka Jerusalem mondo gitim misengini ni Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kweregi.
\v 17 Ne gitego loch Juda kendo kuom higni adek negimiyo Rehoboam wuod Solomon obedo motegno ka giwuotho e yor Daudi kod Solomon e kindeno.
\s1 Joka Rehoboam
\p 
\v 18 Rehoboam nonywomo Mahalath mane nyar wuod Daudi miluongo ni Jerimoth kendo min mare ne en Abihail ma nyar Eliab wuod Jesse.
\v 19 Nonywolone yawuowi magin Jeush, Shemaria kod Zaham.
\v 20 Bangʼe nokendo Maaka nyar Abisalom mane onywolone Abija, Atai, Ziza kod Shelomith.
\v 21 Rehoboam nohero Maaka nyar Abisalom moloyo mondege mamoko kod mon mamoko. Ne en kod mon apar gaboro kaachiel gi mon mamoko piero auchiel, bende ne en gi yawuowi piero ariyo gaboro kod nyiri piero auchiel.
\p 
\v 22 Rehoboam noyiero Abija wuod Maaka obed jatelo e kind owetene mondo omi obed ruoth.
\v 23 Ne otiyo gi rieko kuom keyo yawuote moko e piny jo-Juda kod Benjamin kendo e mier madongo mochiel. Nopogogi mwandu mangʼeny kendo nokendonigi mon mangʼeny.
\c 12
\s1 Shishak omonjo Jerusalem
\p 
\v 1 Bangʼe kane Rehoboam nosegurore motegno kaka ruoth, en kaachiel gi jo-Israel duto negijwangʼo chike Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 2 Nikech negiweyo rito chike Jehova Nyasaye, Shishak ruodh Misri nomonjo Jerusalem e higa mar abich mar loch Ruoth Rehoboam.
\v 3 Nobiro gi geche lweny alufu achiel gi mia ariyo kod jolweny moidho farese alufu piero auchiel kod jolweny mangʼeny ma ok kwanre mawuotho mag jo-Libya gi jo-Suk kod Kush bende nobiro kode koa Misri,
\v 4 mokawo miech Juda mochiel motegno mobiro nyaka Jerusalem.
\p 
\v 5 Eka janabi Shemaya nobiro ir Rehoboam kod jotelo mag Juda mano chokore Jerusalem nimar luoro nomakogi nikech Shishak kendo nowachonegi niya, “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye owacho, ‘Useweya omiyo an bende koro aweyou e lwet Shishak.’ ”
\p 
\v 6 Jotend jo-Israel kod ruoth nobolore kawacho niya, “Jehova Nyasaye ni kare.”
\p 
\v 7 Kane Jehova Nyasaye oneno ni negibolore kamano, wach mar Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Shemaya niya, “Nikech gisebolore e nyima ok anatiekgi to abiro resogi bangʼ ndalo manok. Mirimba ok nool Jerusalem koa e lwet Shishak.
\v 8 Kata kamano ginibed e bwo lochne mondo gingʼe pogruok manie kind tiyona kod tiyone ruodhi mag pinje mamoko.”
\p 
\v 9 Kane Shishak ruodh jo-Misri omonjo Jerusalem, noyako mwandu hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kaachiel gi mwandu mag od ruoth. Nokawo gimoro amora kaachiel gi kuodi mag dhahabu mane Solomon ochuogo.
\v 10 Omiyo Ruoth Rehoboam nochwogo okumbni mag nyinyo mondo oket kar mane okawgo kendo nomiyo jotelo mag jorit mane rito rangach midonjogo e dala ruoth.
\v 11 E kinde moro amora mane ruoth dhi e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, joritogo ne tingʼo kuodigo kendo bangʼe negidwokogi e od jorito.
\p 
\v 12 Nikech Rehoboam nobolore, mirimb Jehova Nyasaye nowuok kuome kendo ne ok otieke chutho. To bende ne nitie gik moko mabeyo Juda.
\p 
\v 13 Ruoth Rehoboam nogurore motegno Jerusalem kendo nodhi nyime kaka ruoth. Ne en ja-higni piero angʼwen gachiel kane obedo ruoth kendo norito piny kuom higni apar gabiriyo ka en Jerusalem dala maduongʼ mane Jehova Nyasaye oseyiero kuom dhout jo-Israel duto mondo Nyinge obedie. Min mare ne nyinge Naama ma nyar jo-Amon.
\v 14 Notimo richo nikech ne ok oketo chunye mondo odwar Jehova Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 15 Kuom weche mag loch Rehoboam aa chakruokgi nyaka gikogi, donge ondikgi e kitap Shemaya janabi kod mar Ido janen mandiko nonro mag ji? Ne nitiere lweny ma ok rum e kind Rehoboam gi Jeroboam.
\v 16 Rehoboam notho kaka kwerene kendo noyike kodgi e Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi. Abija wuode nobedo ruoth kare.
\c 13
\s1 Abija obedo ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 1 E higa mar apar gaboro mar loch Jeroboam, Abija nobedo ruodh Juda,
\v 2 kendo norito piny kuom higni adek kodak Jerusalem. Min mare ne nyinge Maaka ma nyar Uriel ja-Gibea.
\p Ne nitiere lweny e kind Abija kod Jeroboam.
\v 3 Abija nodhi e kedo ka en gi jolweny molony alufu mia angʼwen to Jeroboam nochano jolweny moyier marateke alufu mia aboro.
\p 
\v 4 Abija nochungo e Got Zemaraim e piny gode mag Efraim kowacho niya, “Winjauru in Jeroboam kod jo-Israel duto!
\v 5 Donge ungʼeyo ni Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach jo-Israel nomiyo Daudi kod nyikwaye loch Israel nyaka chiengʼ kotimo kodgi singruok ma ok tow?
\v 6 To kata obedo kamano Jeroboam wuod Nebat jatelo mar Solomon wuod Daudi nongʼanyo ni ruodhe.
\v 7 Ji moko ma timbegi mono noriwore kode mi negikwedo Rehoboam wuod Solomon kane pod en rawera mayom yom kendo ne ok otek monyalo sirogi.
\p 
\v 8 “To koro sani ichano mondo itamri loch Jehova Nyasaye mantiere e lwet nyikwa Daudi. Adieri un kod jolweny mangʼeny kendo un kod nyiroye mag dhahabu mane Jeroboam oloso mondo obed nyisecheu.
\v 9 To donge nuriembo jodolo mag Jehova Nyasaye ma yawuot Harun kaachiel gi jo-Lawi kendo ne uyiero jodolo magu kaka jopinje mamoko timo? Ngʼato angʼata mobiro opwodhore gi nyarwath kod imbe abiriyo nyalo bedo jadolo mar gik ma ok nyiseche.
\p 
\v 10 “Wan to Jehova Nyasaye en Nyasachwa kendo ok waseweye ngangʼ. Jodolo matiyone Jehova Nyasaye gin yawuot Harun kendo jo-Lawi konyogi e tijno.
\v 11 Okinyi godhiambo gichiwone Jehova Nyasaye misengini miwangʼo pep kod gik mangʼwe ngʼar kendo giketo makati e mesa mopwodhi kendo gimoko teche moket e rachungi taya mar dhahabu godhiambo pile ka pile. Wan warito chike Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa, un to useweye.
\v 12 Nyasaye ni kodwa; en e jatendwa. Jodolo mage biro goyo turumbete miluong ji mondo oked kodu. Jo-Israel, kik uked gi Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kwereu nikech ok ubiloyo.”
\p 
\v 13 Jeroboam noseoro jolweny mondo oluor e tokgi mondo ni kane en e nyim Juda to jolweny moko mondo omonjgi gi ka tokgi.
\v 14 Kane jo-Juda olokore moneno nine imonjogi gi ka tokgi kod e nyimgi eka negiywagore ni Jehova Nyasaye. To jodolo bende nogoyo turumbete
\v 15 eka jo-Juda nongʼiyo kendo kane gigiyo kamano Nyasaye nokeyo Jeroboam kaachiel gi jo-Israel duto e nyim Abija kod jo-Juda.
\v 16 Jo-Israel noringo akeya nono e nyim jo-Juda nikech Nyasaye nochiwogi e lwet jo-Juda.
\v 17 Abija kod joge nonegogi malich ahinya ma joma nohinyore kuom jo-Israel marateke moyier ne gin ji alufu mia abich.
\v 18 Kamano e kaka ne olo jo-Israel chiengʼno, jo-Juda nolocho nikech negigeno kuom Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kweregi.
\p 
\v 19 Abija nolawo Jeroboam mokawo mieche kaka Bethel gi Jeshana kod Efron kod mier matindo mokiewo kode.
\v 20 Loch Jeroboam ne ok ochako obedo motegno e kinde Abija. Bangʼe Jehova Nyasaye nogoye motho.
\p 
\v 21 Loch Abija nomedo gurore motegno. Nokendo mon apar gangʼwen kendo ne en gi yawuowi piero ariyo gariyo kod nyiri apar gauchiel.
\p 
\v 22 Weche moko mag loch Abija, timbene duto kod gik mane owacho ondiki e kitap Ido janabi.
\c 14
\p 
\v 1 Kendo Abija notho kaka kwerene kendo noyike e Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi. Asa wuode nobedo ruoth kare kendo e kinde mar lochne ne nitiere kwe kuom higni apar.
\s1 Asa obedo ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 2 Asa notimo gik mabeyo kendo makare e nyim Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache.
\v 3 Nogolo kende mag misango mag pinje ma oko kaachiel gi kuonde motingʼore malo komuko kite milamo kendo ngʼado sirni mag Ashera.
\v 4 Nochiwo ne Juda chik ni mondo omany Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kweregi kendo orit chikene kod buchene.
\v 5 Nomuko kuonde motingʼore malo kod kende mag misango miwangʼoe ubani e miech Juda, kendo pinyruoth nobedo gi kwe e ndalone.
\v 6 Nogero mier madongo mag Juda mochiel gohinga motegno nimar piny ne nigi kwe. Onge ngʼama ne kedo kode ndalogo nikech Jehova Nyasaye nomiye yweyo.
\p 
\v 7 Asa nowacho ne jo-Juda niya, “Wageruru miechgi kendo waket ohinga molworogi man-gi kuonde maboyo mag ngʼicho gi rangeye kod lodi milorogi godo. Piny pod marwa nimar waseluwo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa, newaluwe to en nomiyowa yweyo koni gi koni.” Omiyo negigedo kendo negidhi nyime maber.
\p 
\v 8 Asa ne nigi jolweny ma jo-Juda alufu mia adek moritore gi kuodi madongo kod tonge, kod jo-Benjamin alufu mia ariyo gi piero aboro manoritore gi okumba gi atungʼ. Magi duto ne gin jolweny mathuondi mager.
\p 
\v 9 Zera ja-Kush nomonjogi kod jolweny mangʼeny kaachiel gi geche mag lweny mia adek manobiro nyaka Maresha.
\v 10 Asa nodhi mondo orom kode kendo negikawo kuondegi mag lweny e Holo mar Zefatha man but Maresha.
\p 
\v 11 Eka Asa noywak ne Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache kowacho niya, “Jehova Nyasaye, onge ngʼato moro machalo kodi manyalo konyo joma nyap kuom joma roteke makmana in. Yie ikonywa nikech wageno kuomi yaye Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa kendo wabiro rado gi jolweny mangʼenygi nikech Nyingi. Yaye Jehova Nyasaye in Nyasachwa kik iwe dhano adhana loyi.”
\p 
\v 12 Eka Jehova Nyasaye nonego jo-Kush e nyim Asa kod Juda. Jo-Kush noringo
\v 13 kendo Asa kod jolweny mage nolawogi nyaka Gerar. Jo-Kush mangʼeny nonegi mane ok ginyal konyo nikech Jehova Nyasaye gi jolweny mage ema notimo mano. Jo-Juda noyako gik mangʼeny ahinya.
\v 14 Negiketho mier matindo duto mokiewo gi Gerar nikech luoro moa kuom Jehova Nyasaye nomakogi. Ne giyako mier duto mane ni kanyo nikech ne nitiere gik moko mangʼeny kanyo.
\v 15 Negituro kunde dhok kendo negipeyo rombe, diek kod ngamia mathoth bangʼe negidok Jerusalem.
\c 15
\s1 Asa oloso piny Juda
\p 
\v 1 Roho mar Nyasaye nolor kuom Azaria wuod Oded.
\v 2 Nodhi moromo kod Asa mowachone niya, “Chikuru itu mondo uwinja, in Asa gi jo-Juda duto kod jo-Benjamin. Jehova Nyasaye nikodu ka un bende un kode, kudware to ununwangʼe, to kujwangʼe to en bende nojwangʼu.
\v 3 Kuom kinde marabora jo-Israel ne onge gi Nyasaye ma adier kaachiel gi jadolo mane nyalo puonjogi kendo ne gionge gi chik.
\v 4 To kane gin e thagruok ne giywakne Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel ka gimanye mine giyude.
\v 5 E ndalogo ne ok yot mondo ngʼato owuothi ma ok onwangʼo chandruok e yo, ma ne timore nikech jopiny duto nopongʼ gi chandruok.
\v 6 Oganda moro ne kedo gi oganda machielo kendo dala moro bende ne kedo gi dala moro, nikech Nyasaye nooronigi chandruok mangʼeny.
\v 7 Un to beduru motegno kendo chunyu kik ol nimar nochulu kuom tiju.”
\p 
\v 8 Kane Asa owinjo wechegi to gi koro mar janabi Azaria wuod Oded, notimo chir mogolo nyiseche manono e piny Juda kod Benjamin duto kod mier duto manokawo e gode matindo mag Efraim. Noloso kendo mar misango mar Jehova Nyasaye mane okethore mane nitie e nyim agola mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 9 Bangʼe nochoko jo-Juda duto kod jo-Benjamin kaachiel gi jo-Efraim, jo-Manase kod jo-Simeon manodak e kindgi nimar ji mangʼeny noweyo jo-Israel mobiro ire kane gineno ni Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache nenikode.
\p 
\v 10 Negichokore Jerusalem e dwe mar adek e hik loch Asa mar apar gabich.
\v 11 Chiengʼno negitimone Jehova Nyasaye misango gi dhok mia abiriyo kod rombe kod diek alufu abiriyo mane gin gik mane giyako.
\v 12 Negitimo singruok ni gibiro manyo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kweregi gi chunygi kod ngimagi duto.
\v 13 Jogo duto ma ok noluw Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach jo-Israel, obed ngʼama tin kata maduongʼ, obed dichwo kata dhako nonegi.
\v 14 Negitimo winjruok gi Jehova Nyasaye ka gikok gi dwol maduongʼ, ka gigoyo koko gi turumbete kod tungʼ.
\v 15 Jo-Juda duto nomor kod singruokno nikech negisingore gi chunygi duto. Negimanyo Nyasaye gi chuny achiel kendo negiyude. Omiyo Jehova Nyasaye nomiyogi kwe kuonde duto.
\p 
\v 16 Ruoth Asa nogolo damare Maaka e kome mane entie kaka min ruoth nikech noloso sirni milamo mar Ashera. Asa nongʼado yien-no mokinge matindo tindo mowangʼe e holo mar Kidron.
\v 17 Kata obedo ni Asa ne ok oketho kuonde motingʼore malo mag lemo e Israel, chunye nochiwore chutho ni Jehova Nyasaye ndalo duto mag ngimane.
\v 18 Nokelo gige dhahabu gi fedha kod mula e hekalu mar Nyasaye ma en owuon gi wuon mare nosepwodho.
\p 
\v 19 Ne onge lweny kendo nyaka higa mar piero adek gabich mar loch Asa.
\c 16
\s1 Higni mogik mag Asa
\p 
\v 1 E higa mar piero adek gabich mar loch Asa, Baasha ruodh Israel nodhi kedo kod Juda kendo nochielo Rama motegno mondo ogengʼ ni ngʼato angʼata kik wuogi kata donji e piny Asa ruodh Juda.
\p 
\v 2 Eka Asa nokawo fedha gi dhahabu e kuonde keno mag hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kaachiel gi mago manokano e ode moorogi ne Ben-Hadad ruodh Aram manodak Damaski.
\v 3 Nowachone niya, “Winjruok mondo obedie kindi koda mana kaka nobedo e kind wuonwa gi wuonu. Aoroni mich mag fedha gi dhahabu, koro keth winjruok mantie e kindi gi Baasha ruodh Israel mondo mi owe kedo koda.”
\p 
\v 4 Ben-Hadad noyie gi Ruoth Asa kendo nooro jotende mag lweny mondo omonj mier madongo mag Israel. Negiloyo Ijon, gi Dan kod Abel Maim kaachiel gi mier mag madongo mag keno mag Naftali.
\v 5 Kane Baasha owinjo mano, nochungo gero Rama kendo nojwangʼo tije.
\v 6 Eka Ruoth Asa nokelo jo-Juda duto kendo negikawo kite duto kod yiende mane Baasha osebedo katiyogo Rama kendo notiyo kodgi kuom gero Geba kod Mizpa.
\p 
\v 7 E ndalogo Hanani janen nobiro ir Asa ruodh Juda mowachone niya, “Nikech nigeno kuom ruodh Aram ma ok kuom Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachi, jolweny mag ruodh Aram osetony oa e lweti.
\v 8 Donge jo-Kush kod jo-Libya ne ni kod jolweny motegno man kod geche lweny mangʼeny kod joriemb farese? To kane igeno kuom Jehova Nyasaye, to nochiwogi e lweti.
\v 9 Nimar wenge Jehova Nyasaye ngʼiyo piny duto koni gi koni mondo ojiw joma chunygi oyie kuome chutho. Isetimo gima ofuwo omiyo chakre sani ibiro bedo gi lweny.”
\p 
\v 10 Asa ne iye owangʼ gi janen nikech wachni, nokecho kode ahinya mokete e twech. To bende e ndalogo Asa nochako sando jomoko malit.
\p 
\v 11 Weche mag loch Asa kar, chakruokgi nyaka gikogi, ondikgi e kitap ruodhi mag Juda kod Israel.
\v 12 E higa mar piero adek gochiko mar loch Asa, tuo nogoye gi e tiende, kendo kata obedo ni tuoneno ne lich to e tuoneno ne ok omanyo kony ir Jehova Nyasaye to mana kuom jothieth.
\v 13 Asa notho moyweyo kod kwerene e higa mar piero angʼwen gi achiel mar lochne,
\v 14 kendo negi yike e liel mane okunyo e Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi. Negipiele e kitanda mopongʼ kod gik mangʼwe ngʼar moruw maber kendo negiloso magenga maduongʼ ka imiyego duongʼ.
\c 17
\s1 Jehoshafat ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 1 Jehoshafat wuode nobedo ruoth kare kendo nogurore motegno mondo osir Israel.
\v 2 Noketo jolweny e mier mochiel duto mag Juda kendo nogero kuonde jolweny Juda kaachiel gi miech Efraim mane Asa wuon mare okawo.
\p 
\v 3 Jehova Nyasaye ne ni kod Jehoshafat nikech e ndaloge mokwongo nowuotho e yore mane Daudi wuon mare owuothoe. Ne ok oluwo Baal
\v 4 to nomanyo Nyasach wuon mare kendo noluwo chikene kopogore gi kaka jo-Israel ne timo.
\v 5 Jehova Nyasaye noguro lochne motegno kendo jo-Juda duto nokelo mich ni Jehoshafat mi nobedo kod mwandu mangʼeny kod huma maduongʼ.
\v 6 Chunye nomako weche Jehova Nyasaye, to bende nogolo e Juda kuonde motingʼore gi malo mag lemo e Juda kaachiel gi sirni milamo mag Ashera.
\p 
\v 7 E higa mar adek mar lochne nooro jotelo mage kaka Ben-Hail, Obadia, Zekaria, Nethanel gi Mikaya mondo opuonj e mier mag Juda.
\v 8 Kaachiel kodgi ne nitie jo-Lawi moko kaka: Shemaya gi Nethania gi Zebadia gi Asahel gi Shemiramoth gi Jehonathan gi Adonija gi Tobija kaachiel gi Tob-Adonija kod jodolo Elishama gi Jehoram.
\v 9 Negipuonjo e piny Juda duto ka gitingʼo Kitap Chik mar Jehova Nyasaye ka gilworore e miech Juda duto kendo ka gipuonjo ji.
\p 
\v 10 Luoro mar Jehova Nyasaye nomako pinyruodhi mag pinje molworo Juda, omiyo ne ok gitugo lweny kod Jehoshafat.
\v 11 Jo-Filistia nokelone Jehoshafat mich mopogore opogore to gi fedha; to jo-Arabu nokelone jamni madirom imbe alufu abiriyo gi mia abiriyo kod diek alufu abiriyo gi mia abiriyo.
\p 
\v 12 Jehoshafat nomedo bedo gi teko kendo nogero mier mochiel gohinga motegno kod mier mag keno e Juda.
\v 13 Kendo nokano gik moko mangʼeny e miech Juda. Noketo e Jerusalem jolweny man kod lony mangʼeny e lweny.
\v 14 Ma e kaka nondikgi kaluwore gi anywolagi:
\b
\li1 Koa kuom jo-Juda jotend migepe mag jolweny alufu achiel (1,000) ne en
\li2 Adna mane otelo ne jolweny maroteke alufu mia adek (300,000);
\li2 
\v 15 maluwe ne en Jehohanan mane jatend jolweny alufu mia ariyo gi piero aboro (280,000);
\li2 
\v 16 maluwe ne en Amasia wuod Zikri mane ochiwore kende owuon ne tij Jehova Nyasaye kendo notelo ne ji alufu mia ariyo (200,000).
\li1 
\v 17 Koa e dhood Benjamin ne gin
\li2 Eliada, jalweny mathuon ka en gi ji alufu mia ariyo (200,000) motingʼo atungʼ kod okumbni;
\li2 
\v 18 maluwe ne en Jehozabad mane ni kod ji alufu mia achiel gi piero aboro (180,000) moikore ne lweny.
\b
\m 
\v 19 Magi e joge mane tiyo ne ruoth ka ok okwan jolweny mane oketo e mier madongo mochiel motegno gohinga e piny Juda duto.
\c 18
\s1 Mikaya okoro wach marach kuom Ahab
\p 
\v 1 Jehoshafat koro ne nigi mwandu mangʼeny kod huma malach, bende notimo winjruok gi Ahab kuom kend.
\v 2 Bangʼ higni moko nodhi Samaria limo Ahab. Ahab noyangʼone kaachiel gi joma ne ni kode rombe mangʼeny kod dhok, kendo nokwaye ni mondo oked gi jo-Ramoth Gilead.
\v 3 Ahab ruodh jo-Israel nopenjo Jehoshafat ruodh Juda niya, “Ibiro dhi konya kedo gi jo-Ramoth Gilead?”
\p Jehoshafat nodwoke niya, “Wan joka ngʼato achiel, kendo joga gin jogi, wabiro konyi kedo.”
\v 4 To Jehoshafat bende nowachone ruodh Israel niya, “Mokwongo penj ane Jehova Nyasaye wachni.”
\p 
\v 5 Omiyo ruodh Israel nochoko jonabi kanyakla maromo ji mia angʼwen mopenjogi niya, “Bende wanyalo dhi kedo gi jo-Ramoth Gilead koso kik adhi?”
\p Negidwoke niya, “Dhiuru nikech Nyasaye nochiwe e lwet ruoth.”
\p 
\v 6 To Jehoshafat nopenjo niya, “Donge nitie janabi mar Jehova Nyasaye ka ma dwapenj wach?”
\p 
\v 7 Ruodh Israel nodwoko Jehoshafat niya, “Pod nitie ngʼato achiel manyalo penjonwa Jehova Nyasaye wach, to ok adware nikech ok okor gimoro amora maber kuoma, to kinde duto mana gik maricho. Nyinge en Mikaya wuod Imla.”
\p Jehoshafat nodwoko niya, “Ruoth, ok onego iwach kamano.”
\p 
\v 8 Omiyo ruodh Israel noluongo achiel kuom jodonge mowachone niya, “Dhi piyo iom Mikaya wuod Imla.”
\p 
\v 9 Ruodh Israel kod Jehoshafat ruodh Juda noyudo orwako lepgi mag ruoth ka moro ka moro kuomgi obet e kom duongʼne e kar dino cham mantie e dhoranga Samaria, kendo ne gin kod jonabi duto mane koro e nyimgi.
\v 10 Koro Zedekia wuod Kenana noloso tunge mag nyinyo kolando niya, “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye owacho, ‘Gi chumbegi ibiro chwowo jo-Aram nyaka itiekgi chuth.’ ”
\p 
\v 11 Jonabi mamoko duto bende ne koro wach mana machal kamano. Negiwacho niya, “Monj jo-Ramoth Gilead kendo ilogi, nikech Jehova Nyasaye enokete e lwet ruoth.”
\p 
\v 12 Jaote mane odhi luongo Mikaya nowachone niya, “Jonabi duto osekoro wach achiel machalre, kagiwacho ni gima ber biro timore ni ruoth. In bende yie ikor wach maber kaka gisekorono.”
\p 
\v 13 To Mikaya nowacho niya, “Akwongʼora gi nying Jehova Nyasaye mangima ni, anyalo mana nyise gima Nyasacha owacho.”
\p 
\v 14 Kane Mikaya ochopo, ruoth nopenje niya, “Bende wanyalo dhi mondo waked gi jo-Ramoth Gilead, koso kik wadhi?”
\p Nodwoke niya, “Ked kodgi kendo iyud loch nimar ibiro chiwgi e lweti.”
\p 
\v 15 Ruoth nowachone niya, “Nyaka karangʼo ma anaketi mondo ikwongʼrina gi nying Jehova Nyasaye ni iwacho adiera ma ok miriambo?”
\p 
\v 16 Eka Mikaya nodwoke niya, “Ne aneno jo-Israel duto koke ewi gode mana kaka rombe maonge jakwath, kendo Jehova Nyasaye nowacho ni, ‘Jogi onge gi ruoth. Yie iwe ngʼato ka ngʼato odhi e dalane gi kwe.’ ”
\p 
\v 17 Ruodh Israel nowachone Jehoshafat niya, “Donge nawachoni ni ok okorna gik mabeyo, to okoro mana gik maricho?”
\p 
\v 18 Mikaya nodhi nyime kawacho niya, “Kuom mano winj wach Jehova Nyasaye: Naneno Jehova Nyasaye kobet e kom duongʼne gi jopolo duto ochungo e bathe korachwich gi koracham.
\v 19 Kendo Jehova Nyasaye nowacho ni, ‘En ngʼa mabiro hoyo Ahab ruodh Israel mondo oked gi jo-Ramoth Gilead kendo onege kuno?’
\p “To ngʼato ka ngʼato nochiwo pache.
\v 20 Mogik, roho marach nobiro mochungʼ e nyim Jehova Nyasaye mowacho ni, ‘Abiro hoye.’ ”
\p Jehova Nyasaye nopenje niya, “Ere kaka ibiro hoye?”
\p 
\v 21 Nodwoko niya, “ ‘Abiro dhi mondo abed roho mar miriambo e dho jonabi mage duto.’ ”
\p Jehova Nyasaye nodwoke niya, “ ‘Dhiyo kendo itim kamano nikech in ema ibiro hoye mi iloye.’
\p 
\v 22 “Omiyo koro sani Jehova Nyasaye oseketo roho mar miriambo e dho jonabigi. Jehova Nyasaye osengʼadoni buch masira.”
\p 
\v 23 Eka Zedekia wuod Kenana noa malo mopamo lemb Mikaya. Nopenje niya, “En yo mane ma Roho mar Jehova Nyasaye noluwo kobiro wuoyo kodi?”
\p 
\v 24 Mikaya nodwoke niya, “Ibiro fwenyo chiengʼ ma iniring kidhi pondo e ot maiye.”
\p 
\v 25 Ruodh Israel nogolo chik niya, “Kawuru Mikaya kendo utere ir Amon jatend dala maduongʼ kendo ir Joash wuod ruoth,
\v 26 kendo uwachne ni, ‘Gima ruoth wacho ema: Ket ngʼatni e od twech kendo kik imiye gimoro amora makmana makati kod pi nyaka aduogi kangima.’ ”
\p 
\v 27 Mikaya nowachone niya, “Kidwogo kingima, to kara ok asewuoyo gi dho Jehova Nyasaye.” Bangʼe nomedo wacho niya, “Winjuru wechena un ji duto!”
\s1 Onego Ahab e Ramoth Gilead
\p 
\v 28 Omiyo ruodh Israel gi Jehoshafat ruodh Juda nodhi Ramoth Gilead.
\v 29 Ruodh Israel nowachone Jehoshafat niya, “Abiro rwako lewni moko ka wadhi e lweny mondo kik gifwenya, in to rwak arwaka lepi mag ruoth.” Omiyo ruodh Israel norwako lewni ma ok nyal fwenyego kendo nodhi e lweny.
\p 
\v 30 Ruodh jo-Aram nogolo chik ne jotende mariembo geche niya, “Kik uked gi ngʼato angʼata bed ni otin kata oduongʼ makmana ruodh Israel.”
\v 31 Kane jotelo mariembo geche lweny noneno Jehoshafat negiwacho e chunygi niya, “Nyaka bed ni ma e ruodh Israel.” Omiyo negilokore mondo giked kode, to kane Jehoshafat oywak, Jehova Nyasaye nokonye. Nyasaye nogologi kuome,
\v 32 nikech kane jotelo mariembo geche lweny noneno ni ok en ruodh Israel, negiweyo lawe.
\p 
\v 33 To ngʼat moro noywayo atungʼ mare modiro asere ma nochwowo ruodh Israel e kind law lweny mane orwako. Ruoth nonyiso jariemb gari niya, “Lok garini mondo igola ka, nimar ahinyora marach.”
\v 34 Odiechiengʼno duto lweny nomedo bedo mager kendo noten ruodh Israel e gache komanyore gi jo-Aram nyaka godhiambo mondo ojiw joge. Notho ka chiengʼ dhi podho.
\c 19
\p 
\v 1 Kane Jehoshafat ruodh Juda noduogo ode Jerusalem kongima,
\p 
\v 2 Jehu janen ma wuod Hanani nodhi mondo orom kode kendo nonyiso ruoth niya, “Bende dikony joricho kendo iher jogo mochayo Jehova Nyasaye? Mirimb Jehova Nyasaye ni kuomi nikech isetimo ma.
\v 3 Kata kama nitiere ber moko kuomi nikech isegolo e piny sirni milamo mag Ashera kendo chunyi bende iseketo mondo omany Nyasaye.”
\s1 Jehoshafat oyiero jongʼad bura
\p 
\v 4 Jehoshafat nodak Jerusalem, nochako owuok kendo kolimo joge koa Bersheba nyaka chop piny gode matindo mag Efraim kendo kojiwo chunygi mondo gidwog ir Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kweregi.
\v 5 Noketo jongʼad bura e piny, e mier duto madongo mag Juda mochiel gohinga.
\v 6 Nonyisogi niya, “Paruru malongʼo gima utimo, nikech ok ungʼad bura gi nying dhano to ungʼado e nying Jehova Nyasaye man kodu e seche mungʼadoe bura.
\v 7 Emomiyo tiuru ka luoro mar Nyasaye ni kodu. Ritreuru ka ungʼado bura nimar kuom Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa onge tim marach kata dewo wangʼ kata chulo asoya.”
\p 
\v 8 Bende e Jerusalem, Jehoshafat noketo jo-Lawi, jodolo kaachiel gi jotend anywola moko mag jo-Israel mondo ongʼad bura e nying Jehova Nyasaye kendo mondo gikel kwe e tungni. Kendo negidak Jerusalem.
\v 9 Nochikogi kama, Nyaka uti tijeu gi adiera kendo gi chunyu duto ka uluoro Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 10 Kuom wach moro amora mane okel e nyimu gi joweteu modak e mier, bedni en wach nek kata weche moko mag chik, yorene kata weche mag buchene to nyaka usiemgi ni kik giketh e nyim Jehova Nyasaye, ka ok kamano to mirimbe nobi kuomu kod kuom joweteu. Kutimo ma, to ok unutim richo.
\p 
\v 11 “Amaria jadolo maduongʼ ema notelnu e weche duto mag Jehova Nyasaye, to Zebadia wuod Ishmael ma jatend dhood Juda to notelnu e weche duto mag ruoth, to jo-Lawi noti kaka jotelo kuomu. Tiuru ka un gi chir, kendo Jehova Nyasaye obed gi jogo matimo maber.”
\c 20
\s1 Jehoshafat oloyo jo-Moab kod jo-Amon
\p 
\v 1 Bangʼ mano jo-Moab kod jo-Amon kaachiel gi jo-Meun moko nobiro mondo oked gi Jehoshafat.
\p 
\v 2 Jomoko nobiro monyiso Jehoshafat niya, “Oganda lweny maduongʼ moa Edom bironi koa e loka Nam kocha. Gisechopo Hazazon Tamar” (tiende ni, En Gedi).
\v 3 Jehoshafat nobwok omiyo nokwayo Jehova Nyasaye kendo nochiko jo-Juda duto mondo otwe chiemo.
\v 4 Jo-Juda duto nobiro kaachiel mondo gikwa Jehova Nyasaye kony, adier negia e mier mag Juda duto mondo gidwar wangʼe.
\p 
\v 5 Eka Jehoshafat nochungʼ e nyim oganda mar Juda kod Jerusalem e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye e nyim laru manyien
\v 6 mowacho niya,
\pm “Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kwerewa, donge in e Nyasaye mantie e polo? In ema itelone pinyruodhi duto mag ogendini. Teko gi nyalo ni e lweti, kendo onge ngʼato manyalo siri.
\v 7 Nyasachwa, donge niriembo joma nodak e pinyni ka jo-Israel neno mimiyo nyikwa Ibrahim osiepni pinyni nyaka chiengʼ?
\v 8 Gisedak e pinyni kendo gisegeroni kama ler mar lemo maluongo Nyingi kagiwacho ni,
\v 9 ‘Ka gima rach ogore kuomwa, bed ni en kum gi ligangla kata dera mar tho kata kech, to wabiro chungʼ e nyimi e hekaluni miluongo gi Nyingi kendo wanaywagreni nikech masirani, kendo iniwinjwa mi ireswa.’
\pm 
\v 10 “To koro jo-Amon gi jo-Moab kod jo-Got Seir mane ok iyiene jo-Israel mondo omonj pinygi kane gia Misri; kuom mano ne giweyogi ma ok gitiekogi.
\v 11 Neye gima gitimonwa kuom biro mondo giriembwa e gima nimiyowa kaka girkeni marwa.
\v 12 Nyasachwa, donge dingʼadnegi bura? Wan to waonge kod teko ma wanyalo kedogo kod oganda lweny maduongʼni ma monjowani. Wan ok wangʼeyo gima dwatim, genowa waketo kuomi.”
\p 
\v 13 Jo-Juda duto gi mondegi gi nyithindgi kod nyithindgi matindo nochungʼ e nyim Jehova Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 14 Eka Roho mar Jehova Nyasaye nolor kuom Jahaziel wuod Zekaria ma wuod Benaya, ma wuod Jeyel ma wuod Matania ma ja-Lawi kendo nyakwar Asaf kane ochungʼ e dier chokruok.
\p 
\v 15 Nowacho niya, “Chik iti in Ruoth Jehoshafat kaachiel gi jogo duto modak Juda gi Jerusalem! Jehova Nyasaye wachoni kama: ‘Kik ibed gi luoro kendo chunyi kik parre nikech oganda lweny maduongʼni, nimar lweny ok maru, to en mar Nyasaye.
\v 16 Kiny upangru ka udhi irgi. Gibiro biro ka gitwenyo got ka giluwo Holo mar Ziz kendo ubiro yudogi e giko piny mar kamotuo mar Jeruel.
\v 17 Ok ochuno ni uked e lwenyni. Kawuru kuondeu, chunguru motegno mondo une loch ma Jehova Nyasaye nomiu, yaye Juda kod Jerusalem. Kik ubed maluor, kendo kik chunyu nyosre. Kiny dhiuru mondo urad kodgi nimar Jehova Nyasaye nobed kodu.’ ”
\p 
\v 18 Jehoshafat nokulore piny auma kendo jo-Juda duto kod Jerusalem nogoyo chonggi piny e nyim Jehova Nyasaye ka gilame.
\v 19 Eka jo-Lawi moko, jo-Kohath kod jo-Kora nochungo mopako Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach jo-Israel gi dwol maduongʼ ahinya.
\p 
\v 20 Gokinyi mangʼich negiwuok gidhi e piny Tekoa motwo. Kane giwuok Jehoshafat nochungʼ kawacho niya, “Chikuru itu un jo-Juda kod joma odak Jerusalem! Beduru kod geno kuom Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachu eka unukuwo, bende yieuru gi jonabi mage eka unulo.”
\v 21 Kane osepimo wach gi joge, Jehoshafat noyiero joma onego owerne Jehova Nyasaye mondo gipak berne mokalo apima mar lerne ka gitelo e nyim jolweny ka giwer niya,
\q1 “Dwokneuru Jehova Nyasaye erokamano,
\q2 nikech herane osiko nyaka chiengʼ.”
\p 
\v 22 Kane gichako wer kendo pake, Jehova Nyasaye norundogi ma jo-Amon kod jo-Moab kaachiel gi jo-Got Seir manomonjo Juda nochako kedo kendgi giwegi mi nologi.
\v 23 Jo-Amon gi jo-Moab noriwore mochako kedo kod jo-Got Seir monegogi kendo otiekogi pep. Kane gitieko nego jo-Got Seir, negikonyore kuom tiekore kendgi giwegi.
\p 
\v 24 Kane jo-Juda nobiro kama omanyore gi kama otimo ongoro kendo gingʼiyo oganda lweny maduongʼ, negineno mana ringre joma otho koriere piny kendo ne githo maonge ngʼama notony.
\v 25 Omiyo Jehoshafat gi joge nodhi mondo giyak mwandu kendo neginwangʼo gige lweny mangʼeny kod lewni kod gik moko ma nengogi tek mangʼeny ma ok neginyal tingʼo duto. Gik miyako ne ngʼeny ahinya mane otieko ndalo adek mondo giyakgi duto.
\v 26 To chiengʼ mar angʼwen negichokore e Holo mar Beraka kama ne gipakoe Jehova Nyasaye. Ma emomiyo iluonge ni Holo mar Beraka nyaka chil kawuono.
\p 
\v 27 Eka jo-Juda gi jo-Jerusalem duto kotelnegi kod Jehoshafat nodok Jerusalem ka gimor gi ilo nikech Jehova Nyasaye nomiyogi mor kuom loyo wasikgi.
\v 28 Negidonjo Jerusalem e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye ka gigoyo nyatiti gi asili kod turumbete.
\p 
\v 29 Luoro mar Nyasaye nomako pinjeruodhi mag pinje kane giwinjo kaka Jehova Nyasaye nokedo gi wasik jo-Israel.
\v 30 Kamano pinyruoth Jehoshafat ne nigi kwe nikech Nyasache nomiye yweyo kuonde duto.
\s1 Giko mar loch Jehoshafat
\p 
\v 31 Mano e kaka Jehoshafat norito Juda. Ne en ja-higni piero adek gabich kane obedo ruodh Juda kendo norito piny kodak Jerusalem kuom higni piero ariyo gabich. Min mare ne nyinge Azuba nyar Shilhi.
\v 32 Noluwo yore Asa wuon mare kendo ne ok oweyogi, nimar notimo gima kare e nyim Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 33 To kata kamano kuonde motingʼore gi malo mag lemo ne ok omuki kendo ji ne pok oketo chunygi kuom Nyasach kweregi.
\p 
\v 34 Gik mamoko manotimore e ndalo loch Jehoshafat aa chakruok nyaka gikogi ondikgi e weche mag ndalo mag Jehu wuod Hanani kaka ochan-gi e kitap ruodhi mag Israel.
\p 
\v 35 Bangʼe Jehoshafat ruodh Juda notimo winjruok kod Ahazia ruodh Israel manongʼadne bura nikech timbene maricho.
\v 36 Ne giwinjore ni gihondho yiedhi mangʼeny mag loko ohala. Bangʼe kane oselosgi Ezion Geber,
\v 37 Eliezer wuod Dodavahu ma ja-Maresha nokoro wach marach kuom Jehoshafat kowacho niya, “Nikech isetimo winjruok kod Ahazia, Jehova Nyasaye biro ketho gigo ma iseloso.” Yiedhigo nobarore kendo ne ok ginyal kwangʼ mondo gitim ohala.
\c 21
\p 
\v 1 Jehoshafat notho kaka kwerene kendo noyike but kwerene e Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi kendo Jehoram wuode nobedo ruoth kare.
\v 2 Owete Jehoram ma yawuot Jehoshafat ne gin Azaria gi Jehiel gi Zekaria kod Azariahu gi Mikael kod Shefatia. Magi duto ne gin yawuot Jehoshafat ruodh Israel.
\v 3 Wuon-gi nosemiyogi mwandu mangʼeny mag fedha gi dhahabu gi gik moko ma nengogi tek kaachiel gi mier mag Juda mochiel gohinga motegno, kata kamano loch pinye nomiyo Jehoram pinyruoth nikech ne en wuode makayo.
\s1 Jehoram ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 4 Kane Jehoram nosegurore motegno e kom duongʼ wuon mare, nonego owetene gi ligangla kaachiel gi joka dhood ruoth mamoko mag Israel.
\v 5 Jehoram ne ja-higni piero adek gariyo kane obedo ruoth, kendo norito piny kodak Jerusalem kuom higni aboro.
\v 6 Noluwo timbe mag ruodhi Israel mana kaka jood Ahab notimo nimar nokendo nyar Ahab. Notimo timbe mamono e nyim Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 7 Kata kamano Jehova Nyasaye ne ok otieko od Daudi nikech noparo singruok mane otimo kode. Nosesingore ne Daudi gi ogandane ni ginibed e loch nyaka chiengʼ.
\p 
\v 8 E ndalo loch Jehoram, Edom nongʼanyo ne Juda mi gibedo gi ruodhgi giwegi.
\v 9 Omiyo Jehoram nodhi kuno gi jotende kod gechene duto mag lweny. Jo-Edom nolwore kaachiel gi jotend gechene mag lweny, to nochiewo gotieno momwomogi.
\v 10 Nyaka chil kawuono jo-Edom pod ongʼanyo ne jo-Juda.
\p Jo-Libna bende nongʼanyo e ndalono nikech Jehoram noweyo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kwerene.
\v 11 Bende ne osegero kuonde motingʼore malo mag lemo e gode matindo mag Juda kendo nomiyo jo-Jerusalem oweyo Nyasaye kendo omiyo jo-Juda bende orwenyo.
\p 
\v 12 Jehoram nonwangʼo baruwa koa ir Elija janabi mawacho niya,
\pm “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kwaru Daudi wacho, ‘Ok iseluwo yore wuonu Jehoshafat kata mago mag Asa ruodh Juda.
\v 13 To isewuotho e yore mag ruodhi mag Israel, omiyo isemiyo jo-Juda kod jo-Jerusalem oseweyo luwa mana kaka dhood Ahab notimo. Bende isenego oweteni monywoligo ma nyithind wuonu hie, joma ne ber moloyi.
\v 14 Koro omiyo Jehova Nyasaye biro chwado jogi, yawuoti kod mondi kod gimoro amora miluongo ni mari, noyud chwat malit.
\v 15 In iwuon nibed gi tuo marach manocham nyimbiyi, kendo tuoni nomi nyimbiyi wuog oko.’ ”
\p 
\v 16 Jehova Nyasaye nomiyo jo-Filistia gi jo-Arabu modak mokiewo kod jo-Kush obedo mamono kod Jehoram.
\v 17 Negimonjo Juda magi kedo kode kendo negipeyo gik moko duto mane nitie e od ruoth kaachiel gi yawuote kod monde. Onge wuode mane odongʼ makmana wuode ma chogo miluongo ni Ahazia.
\p 
\v 18 Bangʼ mano Jehova Nyasaye nogoyo Jehoram gi tuo malich momako nyimbiye ma ok thiedhre.
\v 19 Bangʼ kinde manok madirom higni ariyo, tuone nomedore ma nyimbiye nowuok oko omiyo notho ka en gi rem malich. Joge ne ok olosone mach mar magenga kaka nolosne kwerene.
\p 
\v 20 Jehoram ne ja-higni piero adek gariyo ka nodoko ruoth, kendo norito piny kuom higni aboro kodak Jerusalem. Notho maonge ngʼama nokuyo kuom thone kendo noyike e Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi to ok kuma iyikoe ruodhi.
\c 22
\s1 Loch Ahazia ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 1 Jo-Jerusalem noketo Ahazia wuod Jehoram ma chogo nobedo ruoth kare nikech joma nomonjogi kaachiel gi jo-Arabu manobiro e lwenyno nosenego yawuot Jehoram madongo duto. Omiyo Ahazia wuod Jehoram ruodh Juda nochako rito loch.
\p 
\v 2 Ahazia ne ja-higni piero ariyo gariyo kane obedo ruoth kendo norito piny kuom higa achiel kodak Jerusalem. Min mare ne nyinge Athalia ma nyakwar Omri.
\p 
\v 3 En bende noluwo timbe mag od Ahab nimar min mare nojiwe mondo otim timbe maricho.
\v 4 Notimo timbe mamono e nyim Jehova Nyasaye mana kaka jood Ahab nosetimo nikech bangʼ tho wuon mare gin ema ne gingʼadone rieko marach mane okethe.
\v 5 Bende noluwo puonjgi kane oriwore gi Joram wuod Ahab ruodh Israel mondo giked kod Hazael ruodh Aram e piny Ramoth Gilead. Jo-Aram nohinyo Joram;
\v 6 omiyo nodok Jezreel mondo ochangi kuom hinyruok manoyudo Ramoth ka nokedo gi Hazael ruodh Aram.
\p Eka Ahazia wuod Jehoram ruodh Juda nodhi Jezreel mondo one Joram wuod Ahab nikech nohinye.
\p 
\v 7 To Nyasaye nosechano mondo otiek Ahazia kodhi limo Joram. Kane Ahazia ochopo negidhi gi Joram mondo girom gi Jehu wuod Nimshi mane Jehova Nyasaye osewiro mondo otiek dhood Ahab.
\v 8 Kane Jehu ngʼado bura ni dhood Ahab, nonwangʼo yawuot ruoth moa e dhood ruodhi mag Juda kaachiel gi yawuot wede Ahazia mane osebedo katiyone kendo nonegogi.
\v 9 Bangʼe nodhi mondo omany Ahazia kendo joge nonwangʼe kopondo Samaria. Nokele ne Jehu mine onege. Ne giike kagiwacho niya, “Ne en wuod Jehoshafat manoluwo Jehova Nyasaye gi chunye duto.” Omiyo ne onge ngʼato moro amora motegno e od Ahazia mane nyalo rito piny.
\s1 Athalia kod Joash
\p 
\v 10 Kane Athalia min Ahazia noneno ni wuode osetho, nodhi mondo otiek anywola mar joka ruoth mar Juda duto.
\v 11 To Jehosheba nyar ruoth Jehoram nokawo Joash wuod Ahazia kendo nokwale lingʼ-lingʼ kuom nyithi ruoth mane idwaro nego mopande e od nindo kaachiel gi japite. Nikech Jehosheba nyar ruoth Jehoram mane chi Jehoyada jadolo ne nyamin Ahazia, nopando nyathino ne Athalia mondo kik onege.
\v 12 Nodongʼ kopande ei hekalu mar Nyasaye kuom higni auchiel e kinde loch Athalia.
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 E higa mar abiriyo Jehoyada nonyiso tekone. Ne otimo winjruok kod jotend migepe mag jolweny mia achiel magin Azaria wuod Jeroham gi Ishmael wuod Jehohanan gi Azaria wuod Obed gi Maseya wuod Adaya kaachiel gi Elishafat wuod Zikri.
\v 2 Ne giwuotho e piny Juda duto ka gichoko jo-Lawi kaachiel gi jotend anywola mag Israel moa e mier duto. Kane gibiro Jerusalem,
\v 3 jogo mano chokore notimo winjruok gi ruoth e hekalu mar Nyasaye.
\p Jehoyada nowachonegi niya, “Wuod ruoth nobed e loch kaka Jehova Nyasaye nosingore kuom nyikwa Daudi.
\v 4 Koro gima onego utim ema: Achiel kuom adek mar jodolo kod jo-Lawi mabiro dhiyo e tich chiengʼ Sabato biro rito dhoudi,
\v 5 to achiel kuom adek machielo to orit od ruoth, to achiel kuom adek modongʼ to orit Ranga Mise to ji mamoko modongʼ duto to nobed e laru mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 6 Kik uyiene ngʼato angʼata mondo odonj e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye makmana jodolo kod jo-Lawi mopwodhi kendo tiyo odiechiengʼno, to ji mamoko duto to orit tije ma Jehova Nyasaye osemiyogi mondo gitim.
\v 7 Jo-Lawi nochungʼ kolworo ruoth ka moro ka moro otingʼo gige lweny mage e lwete kendo ngʼato angʼata modonjo e hekalu nyaka negi, bende beduru machiegni gi ruoth kamoro amora modhiye.”
\p 
\v 8 Jo-Lawi gi jo-Juda notimo kaka Jehoyada jadolo nochikogi. Jatend migawo ka migawo nokawo joge mane dhi tich chiengʼ Sabato to gi mago mane onego oywe, nikech Jehoyada ne ok omiyo migepe mamokogi thuolo.
\v 9 Eka nomiyo jotend migepe mag jolweny mia achiel tonge kod kuodi kod okumba mano mane mag Ruoth Daudi mane nitie e hekalu mar Nyasaye.
\v 10 Nochano ji duto mondo orit ruoth ka moro ka moro nigi gire mar lweny e lwete, chakre yo milambo nyaka yo nyandwat mar hekalu ka gilworo kendo mar misango kod hekalu.
\p 
\v 11 Eka Jehoyada kod yawuote nogolo wuod ruoth oko mi osidhone osimbo mar loch kendo negimiye kitap chik mi gikete ruoth. Ne giwire ka gigoyo koko niya, “Ruoth mondo odag amingʼa!”
\p 
\v 12 Kane Athalia owinjo koko mar joma ne ringo kendo pako ruoth, nodhi irgi e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 13 Nongʼicho moneno ruoth kochungʼ e bath siro mar dhoot. Jotelo gi jogo turumbete nochungʼ e bath ruoth kendo ji duto mag pinyno ne mor kendo negigoyo turumbete, to jower magoyo thumbe notelo ni wende pak. Eka Athalia noyiecho lepe kakok niya, “Andhoga! Andhoga!”
\p 
\v 14 Jehoyada nooro jotelo morito migepe mag jolweny mia achiel-ka, ma bende ne gin jotend jolweny kowachonegi niya, “Keleuru e dierwa kendo neguru ngʼato angʼata maluwe.” Nimar jadolo nosewacho niya, “Kik dhakono donj ei hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.”
\v 15 Omiyo negimake kane ochopo e dhorangaj Farese e kar od ruoth kendo kanyo ema neginege.
\p 
\v 16 Eka Jehoyada gi ji kod ruoth nosingore ni ginibed jo-Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 17 Ji duto nodhi e hekalu mar Baal kendo negimuke. Negitoyo matindo tindo kende mag misango kaachiel gi nyisechene manono kendo neginego Matan jadolo mar Baal e nyim kendegi mag misango.
\p 
\v 18 Bangʼe Jehoyada noketo jorit mag hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye e bwo jodolo mane gin jo-dhood Lawi mane Daudi omiyo tij hekalu mondo gichiw misengini miwangʼo pep ni Jehova Nyasaye kaka ondikgi e Chik Musa ka gimor kod wer kaka Daudi ne ochikogi.
\v 19 Bende noketo jorit dhoudi e rangeye mag hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye mondo ngʼato angʼata ma ok ler kik donji.
\p 
\v 20 Nokawo jotend migepe mag jolweny mia achiel-ka, jood ruoth, jotend ji kaachiel gi jopinyno duto kendo negigolo ruoth oko mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye. Negidhi e od ruoth ka giluwo Rangach Mamalo kendo giketo ruoth e kom duongʼne.
\v 21 Jopinyno duto nobedo gi mor kendo dala maduongʼ nobedo gi kwe, nikech Athalia nosenegi gi ligangla.
\c 24
\s1 Joash oloso kuonde momukore e hekalu
\p 
\v 1 Joash ne ja-higni abiriyo kane odoko ruoth kendo norito piny kuom higni piero angʼwen kodak Jerusalem. Min mare ne nyinge Zibia mane nyar Bersheba.
\v 2 Joash notimo gima kare e nyim wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye e ndalo duto mane Jehoyada jadolo.
\v 3 Jehoyada nogamone mon ariyo manonywologo yawuowi kod nyiri.
\p 
\v 4 Bangʼ ndalo manok Joash noparo mondo olos hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 5 Nochoko jonabi kod jo-Lawi kanyakla achiel kowachonegi niya, Dhiuru e miech Juda kendo usol pesa ma jo-Israel owinjore ogol higa ka higa mondo walosgo hekalu mar Nyasachu. Neuru ni utimo mano mapiyo. To jo-Lawi ne ok otimo mapiyo.
\p 
\v 6 Omiyo ruoth noluongo Jehoyada jadolo maduongʼ mopenje niya, “Angʼo mosemoni oro jo-Lawi mondo osol osuru manoket gi Musa jatich Jehova Nyasaye kod jodong Israel kuom jo-Juda gi jo-Jerusalem mondo olosgo Hemb Romo?”
\p 
\v 7 Koro yawuot Athalia dhako marachno noseketho hekalu mar Nyasaye kendo negitiyo ni Baal gi gik mopwodhi mag Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 8 Bangʼe ruoth nogolo chik mondo olos sanduku, kendo okete e dhoranga hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 9 Noor wach mondo oland ne jo-Juda gi jo-Jerusalem ni mondo gikelne Jehova Nyasaye osuru mane Musa jatich Nyasaye ochiko jo-Israel e thim.
\v 10 Jotelo kod ji duto nokelo pokgi gi mor ka giketogi e sandugno nyaka nopongʼ thich.
\v 11 E kinde ka kinde kane jo-Lawi okelo sanduku ne jotend ruoth kendo kane gineno ni pesa ne nitiere mangʼeny, to jagoro mar joka ruoth kod jatelo margi kod jatij jadolo maduongʼ ne jobiro mondo okaw sanduku kendo kane giseloko gik manie sanduku negidwoke kare. Kamano e kaka negitimo pile ka pile kendo negichoko pesa mangʼeny mokalo.
\v 12 Ruoth kod Jehoyada nochiwo pesa ne jogo mane timo tich mane dwarore mar loso hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye. Negindiko jogedo kod jopa bao kaachiel gi joma olony e tich nyinyo kod mula mondo olos hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 13 Jogo mane rito tich ne ngʼiyo tich maber kendo tich nodhi maber e lwetgi. Negiloso hekalu mar Nyasaye kaluwore gi kaka nogere chon kendo negimedo sire mondo omed bedo motegno.
\v 14 Kane gisetieko, negikelo pesa mane odongʼ ne ruoth kod Jehoyada mi negiloso gik moko mitiyogo e lemo ei hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kaka: gik mitiyogo e misango miwangʼo pep kaachiel gi dise to gi gik mamoko molos gi dhahabu kod fedha. Negitimo misengini miwangʼo pep mapile pile e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kinde duto ka Jehoyada pod ngima.
\p 
\v 15 Jehoyada koro noti kendo hike noniangʼ mine otho ka en ja-higni mia achiel gi piero adek.
\v 16 Ne oike e Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi gi ruodhi nikech gigo mabeyo mane osetimo ni Nyasaye kod hekalu e Israel.
\s1 Timbe Joash maricho
\p 
\v 17 Bangʼ tho Jehoyada, jotend jo-Juda nobiro mondo olim ruoth mi nowinjogi.
\v 18 Negijwangʼo hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kweregi kendo negilamo sirni milamo mag Ashera kod nyiseche manono. Mirima nomako Nyasaye gi jo-Juda gi jo-Jerusalem nikech richogi.
\v 19 Kata obedo ni Jehova Nyasaye nooronegi jonabi mondo odwokgi ire kendo osiemgi malit, to ne gidagi winjo.
\p 
\v 20 Eka Roho mar Nyasaye nolor kuom Zekaria wuod Jehoyada jadolo. Nochungʼ e nyim ji kowacho niya, “Nyasaye wacho kama: ‘Angʼo momiyo ok urito chike Jehova Nyasaye? Omiyo ok unuyud hawi nikech useweyo Jehova Nyasaye omiyo en bende oseweyou.’ ”
\p 
\v 21 To ne giriwore ka gikwedo Zekaria mi negichiele kod kite e laru mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kaka ne ruoth omiyogi chik; mi notho.
\v 22 Ruoth Joash ne ok oparo ngʼwono mane Jehoyada wuon Zekaria notimone, to nonego wuode mane otho kaywak niya, “Mad Jehova Nyasaye ne gima itimona kendo ochulni kuor.”
\p 
\v 23 Kar chak higa, jolweny mag Aram nobiro monjo Joash, negimonjo Juda kod Jerusalem kendo neginego jotendgi duto kendo mwandu mane giyako ne giorone ruodhgi Damaski.
\v 24 Kata obedo ni jolweny mag Aram ne nok moloyo, Jehova Nyasaye nochiwo jo-Juda e lwetgi mana ka gima ne gin jolweny mangʼeny. Nikech Juda noweyo luwo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kweregi kendo nongʼadne Joash bura.
\v 25 Kane jo-Aram osea ne giweyo ka gihinyo Joash malit. Eka jodonge noriworene nikech nek mane onegogo wuod Jehoyada jadolo mi neginege e kitandane. Omiyo notho kendo ne giike e Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi to ok kar yiko ruodhi.
\p 
\v 26 Jogo mane oriworene ne gin Zabad wuod Shimeath nyar Amon kod Jehozabad wuod Shimrith nyar Moab.
\v 27 Weche mane ondiki kuom yawuote gi weche mane jonabi okoro kuome kaachiel gi kaka noloso hekalu mar Nyasaye ondiki e kitap weche mag ndalo mar ruodhi. Kendo Amazia wuode nobedo ruoth kare.
\c 25
\s1 Amazia ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 1 Amazia ne ja-higni piero ariyo gabich kane odoko ruoth kendo norito Jerusalem kuom higni piero ariyo gochiko. Min mare ne nyinge Jehoadin nyar Jerusalem.
\v 2 Notimo gima kare e nyim Jehova Nyasaye to ok gi chunye duto.
\v 3 Bangʼ ka pinyruodhe nosegurore maber, nonego jotelo mane onego wuon mare mane ruoth.
\v 4 Kata kamano ne ok onego yawuot jogo nikech noluwo chik manie Kitap Chik mar Musa mane Jehova Nyasaye oketo mawacho niya, “Wuone ok nonegi nikech ketho mag nyithindgi, bende nyithindo kik negi nikech ketho mag wuonegi, to ngʼato ka ngʼato nonegi nikech richone owuon.”
\p 
\v 5 Eka Amazia nochoko jo-Juda kod jo-Benjamin kaachiel mopogogi tich kaluwore gi anywolagi kendo noyiero jotend migepe mag jolweny alufu achiel kod migepe mag mia achiel. Bangʼe nokwano jogo mahikgi piero ariyo ka dhi nyime kendo nonwangʼo ni ne gin ji alufu mia adek mane nyalo dhi e lweny kendo mane nyalo kedo gi tongʼ kod okumba.
\v 6 Bende nondiko jo-Israel mathuondi alufu mia achiel kochulo fedha ma pekne romo kilo alufu adek gi mia angʼwen.
\p 
\v 7 To ngʼat Nyasaye moro nobiro ire mowachone niya, “Ruoth momi luor, kik iyie mondo jolweny ma jo-Israel dhi kodi nimar Jehova Nyasaye ok ni kod jo-Israel ma jo-Efraim-gi.
\v 8 To kata kidhi ma ikedo gi chir e lweny, to Nyasaye nomi wasiki loyi, nikech Nyasayeno nigi teko mar konyi kata miyo wasiki loyi.”
\p 
\v 9 Amazia nopenjo ngʼat Nyasaye niya, “To wabiro timo angʼo kuom fedha mapekgi romo kilo alufu adek gi mia angʼwen mane wachulo kuom jolweny mag jo-Israel?”
\p Ngʼat Nyasaye nodwoko niya, “Jehova Nyasaye nyalo miyi mangʼeny moloyo mano.”
\p 
\v 10 Eka Amazia noriembo jolweny mane oa Efraim mine gidok e miechgi ka igi owangʼ kendo gikecho malich gi Juda.
\p 
\v 11 To Amazia notimo chir kendo nowuok motelone jolweny mage kagidhi e Holo mar Chumbi kama nonege jo-Seir alufu apar.
\v 12 Jolweny mag Juda nomako ji alufu apar kangima mi negiterogi ewi lwanda moro kendo negidirogi piny ma githo kendo gitur matindo tindo.
\p 
\v 13 To e sechego jolweny mane Amazia oriembo ni ok inyal dhi kode e lweny nomonjo miech Juda chakre Samaria nyaka Beth Horon. Neginego ji alufu adek kendo negipeyo gik moko mangʼeny.
\p 
\v 14 Kane Amazia odwogo koa nego jo-Edom nokelo nyiseche mag jo-Seir moketogi ka nyisechege kokulore nigi kendo notimonigi misango.
\v 15 Jehova Nyasaye nokecho ahinya gi Amazia kendo noorone janabi manowachone niya, “Angʼo momiyo igeno kuom nyiseche mag jogi mane ok nyal reso jogi giwegi e lweti?”
\p 
\v 16 Kane pod janabino wuoyo, ruoth nowachone niya, “Bende waseketi jangʼad rieko ne ruoth? Lingʼ thi! Koso idwaro tho?”
\p Omiyo janabi nolingʼ, to bangʼe nowacho niya, “Angʼeyo ni Nyasaye osechano ni mondo otieki nikech gima isetimo kendo ok isewinjo puonjna.”
\p 
\v 17 Bangʼe Amazia ruodh Juda nopenjo jongʼadne rieko mi nooro joote ir Jehoash wuod Jehoahaz ma wuod Jehu ruoth Israel kowacho niya, “Bi warom wangʼ gi wangʼ.”
\p 
\v 18 To Jehoash ruodh Israel nodwoko Amazia ruodh Juda gi ngero niya, “Kuth alii man Lebanon nooro wach ne yiend sida man Lebanon ni, ‘Yie ichiw nyari ne wuoda mondo okendi.’ To le moro mar bungu mowuok Lebanon nokadho kanyo monyono kuth aliino gi tiende.
\v 19 In iwuorori ni iseloyo jo-Edom kendo koro iwuoyo marach kisungori. To ber mondo ibed mana e dala. Angʼo momiyo imanyo lweny mabiro tieki kaachiel gi jo-Juda duto?”
\p 
\v 20 Kata kamano, Amazia ne ok odewo, nimar ne en dwaro Nyasaye mondo ochiwe e lwet Jehoash nikech negiluwo nyiseche mag Edom.
\v 21 Omiyo Jehoash ruodh Israel nomonje. Jehoash kod Amazia ruodh Juda ne joromo e lweny e dala mar Beth Shemesh man Juda.
\v 22 Jo-Israel noloyo jo-Juda kendo ngʼato ka ngʼato noringo kochomo dalane.
\v 23 Jehoash ruodh Israel nomako Amazia wuod Joash ma wuod Ahazia, ruodh Juda e Beth Shemesh. Bangʼe Jehoash nokele Jerusalem kendo nomuko ohinga mar Jerusalem chakre e Dhoranga Efraim nyaka kama ohinga ogomogo, bor kama ne omuko ne romo fut mia abich gi piero ochiko gachiel.
\v 24 Nokawo dhahabu gi fedha duto kod gik moko duto mane oyudo e hekalu mar Nyasaye mane Obed-Edom orito kaachiel gi keno mar ruoth kod ji moko mano mako e lweny, bangʼe nodok e piny Samaria.
\p 
\v 25 Amazia wuod Joash ruodh Juda nodak higni apar gabich bangʼ tho Jehoash wuod Jehoahaz ruodh Israel.
\v 26 To weche mamoko mag loch Amazia kar chakruokgi nyaka gikogi donge ondikgi e kitap ruodhi mag Juda kod Israel?
\v 27 Chakre ndalo mane Amazia oweyo luwo Jehova Nyasaye, negichikone obadho e Jerusalem mi oringo odhi Lakish, to negioro ji bangʼe Lakish ma onege kuno.
\v 28 Noduog ringre kotingʼ gi faras kendo noyike but kwerene e Dala Maduongʼ mar Juda.
\c 26
\s1 Uzia ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 1 Bangʼe jo-Juda duto nokawo Uzia mane ja-higni apar gauchiel kendo negikete ruoth kar wuon mare Amazia.
\v 2 Kane wuon mare osetho moike kaka kwerene, nochako ogero Elath moduoke ne jo-Juda.
\p 
\v 3 Uzia ne ja-higni apar gauchiel kane odoko ruoth kendo nobedo ruoth kodak Jerusalem kuom higni piero abich gariyo. Min mare ne nyinge Jekolia ma nyar Jerusalem.
\v 4 Notimo gima kare e nyim wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye mana kaka wuon-gi Amazia nosetimo.
\v 5 Noketo chunye kuom Nyasaye e ndalo mag Zekaria, ngʼat ma nopuonje luoro Nyasaye. E ndalo duto mane odwaro Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasaye nomiye gweth.
\p 
\v 6 Nodhi kedo kod jo-Filistia momuko ohinga mar Gath gi Jabne kod Ashdod. Bangʼe nogero mier machiegni kod Ashdod, kod kuonde mamoko ei piny Filistia.
\v 7 Nyasaye nokonye loyo jo-Filistia kod jo-Arabu mane odak Gur Baal kod jo-Meun.
\v 8 Jo-Amon nokelo osuru ne Uzia kendo humbe nolandore nyaka e tongʼ-gi kod jo-Misri nimar nosedoko ngʼama duongʼ ahinya.
\p 
\v 9 Uzia nogero kuonde maboyo mag ngʼicho Jerusalem e Dhorangach miluongo ni Ranga Kama Ohinga Ogomogo gi Ranga Holo kod e giko ohinga kendo nogerogi motegno.
\v 10 E piny motimo ongoro bende nogeroe kuonde motingʼore mag siro lweny kendo nokunyo yewni mangʼeny nikech ne en kod jamni mangʼeny e tie gode kod e piny pap. Bende ne en kod joma ne tiyone e puothe kod puothene mag mzabibu manie gode kaachiel gi kuonde momew nikech nohero pur.
\p 
\v 11 Uzia ne ni kod jolweny motiegore maber moikore dhiye kedo kaluwore kod migepegi mana kaka Jeyel jagoro kod Maseya jatelo nopogogi kaluwore kaka Hanania mane achiel kuom jodong ruoth nochikogi.
\v 12 Kar romb jotelo mag anywola mane otelo ne jolweny ne gin alufu ariyo gi mia auchiel.
\v 13 Jogo mane gitelonegi ne gin jolweny mane otieg ne lweny ne gin ji alufu mia adek gabiriyo kod mia abich, joma ngʼeny moloyo madikony ruoth kedo gi wasike.
\v 14 Uzia noloso ni jolweny kuodi gi tonge gi ogute gi akor mag nyinyo gi atunge gi kite midiro gorujre.
\v 15 Noloso gir lweny moro midirogo aserni gi kite madongo mane joma riek ofwenyo moketo kuonde maboyo mag ngʼicho kod kuonde ma ohinga ogomogo Jerusalem. Humbe nolandore mabor kendo malach nikech nokonye ahinya nyaka nobedo motegno miwuoro.
\p 
\v 16 Kane Uzia osedoko motegno, sungruokne nomiyo opodho. Noweyo luwo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache mi nodonjo e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye mondo owangʼ ubani e kendo mar misango mar ubani.
\v 17 To Azaria jadolo kod jodolo mamoko mag Jehova Nyasaye piero aboro ma jochir noluwe kuno.
\v 18 Negikwere kagiwacho niya, “Uzia, ok en tiji wangʼo ni Jehova Nyasaye ubani; nimar mano en tij jodolo ma nyikwa Harun mane opwodhi mondo giwangʼ ubani. Wuogi e kama ler mar lemo nikech iseketho, omiyo Jehova Nyasaye ok nogwedhi.”
\p 
\v 19 Uzia mane oyudo ka oikore gi tap mach e lwete mondo owangʼ ubani nokecho. Kane mirima omake kod jodolo, dhoho nolandore e lela wangʼe e nyim jodolo e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye but kendo mar misango miwangʼoe ubani.
\v 20 Kane Azaria jadolo maduongʼ gi jodolo duto norange, negineno ni en kod dhoho e lela wangʼe mine gigole oko mapiyo. To en owuon bende noreto mapiyo mondo owuogi nikech Jehova Nyasaye nosechwade.
\p 
\v 21 Ruoth Uzia nobedo ja-dhoho nyaka chiengʼ thone, emomiyo nodak e ot kar kende ka en gi dhoho kendo ne ok oyiene donjo e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye. Jotham wuode ema ne rito dala ruoth kendo norito piny.
\p 
\v 22 Weche mamoko mag loch Uzia koa chakruokgi nyaka gikogi ondikgi e kitap janabi Isaya wuod Amoz.
\v 23 Uzia notho moyweyo gi kwerene kendo noyike machiegni gi paw liete ruodhi nikech ji nowacho niya, “Ne en kod dhoho.” Kendo Jotham wuode nobedo ruoth kare.
\c 27
\s1 Jotham ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 1 Jotham ne ja-higni piero ariyo gabich kane odoko ruoth kendo norito piny kuom higni apar gauchiel kodak Jerusalem. Min mare ne nyinge Jerusha nyar Zadok.
\v 2 Notimo gima kare e nyim wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye mana kaka Uzia wuon mare nosetimo, to mopogore kod wuon mare ne ok odonjo e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye. Kata kamano ji nosiko katimo timbe maricho.
\v 3 Jotham nogero kendo Rangach Mamalo mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye bende nongʼinyore gi tich e ohinga e got matin mar Ofel.
\v 4 Nogero mier e gode matindo mag Juda kod kuonde moger motegno mag jolweny gi kuonde moger motingʼore gi malo mag ngʼicho e bunge.
\p 
\v 5 Jotham notugo lweny gi ruodh jo-Amon mi noloyogi. E higano jo-Amon nochule fedha ma pekne dirom kilo alufu adek gi mia angʼwen kod shairi kilo alufu ariyo gi mia ariyo kod thowi ma pekne ne romo kilo alufu ariyo gi mia ariyo. Jo-Amon nomedo kelone gik marom kamano e higa mar ariyo kod mar adek.
\p 
\v 6 Jotham nomedo bedo gi teko nikech ne owuotho maonge mibadhi e nyim Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache.
\p 
\v 7 Weche mamoko duto mag ndalo loch Jotham, kaachiel gi lwenje mane okedo kod gik moko duto mane otimo, ondiki e kitap ruodhi mag Israel kod Juda.
\v 8 Ne en ja-higni piero ariyo gabich kane odoko ruoth kendo norito piny kuom higni apar gauchiel kodak Jerusalem.
\v 9 Jotham nonindo moyweyo gi kwerene kendo noyike e Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi. Kendo Ahaz ma wuode nobedo ruoth kare.
\c 28
\s1 Ahaz ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 1 Ahaz ne ja-higni piero ariyo kane obedo ruoth kendo nobedo e loch kodak Jerusalem kuom higni apar gauchiel kodak Jerusalem. To timbene ne ok longʼo e nyim wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye kaka timbe Daudi kwar mare ne chalo.
\v 2 Noluwo timbe ruodhi mag Israel kendo nothedho kido milamogo Baal.
\v 3 Notimo liswa e Holo mar Ben Hinom kendo nochiwo nyithinde e mach kaka misango miwangʼo pep koluwo timbe mamono mag ogendini mane Jehova Nyasaye oriembo e nyim jo-Israel.
\v 4 Notimo misengini kendo owangʼo ubani mangʼwe ngʼar e kuonde motingʼore malo mag lemo, ewi gode matindo kendo e bwo yiende motimo otiep.
\p 
\v 5 Omiyo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache nochiwe e lwet ruodh Aram mi jo-Aram noloye kendo nomako joge mangʼeny kaka joma otwe kendo noterogi Damaski.
\p Bende nochiwe e lwet ruodh Israel, mane onego joge mangʼeny.
\v 6 Kuom odiechiengʼ achiel Peka wuod Remalia nonego jolweny mag Juda alufu achiel nikech Juda nosejwangʼo Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kweregi.
\v 7 Zikri thuon Efraim nonego Maseya wuod ruoth kod Azrikam jatelo mane ochungʼ ne od ruoth kod Elkana mane jalup ruoth.
\v 8 Jo-Israel nomako owetegi alufu mia ariyo mane gin mon kod yawuowi kod nyiri. Bende ne giyako mwandu mangʼeny mane gitingʼo gidwoko Samaria.
\p 
\v 9 To noyudo ka janabi mar Jehova Nyasaye ma nyinge Oded ne ni kanyo kendo nodhi moromo kod jolweny kane gidwogo Samaria. Nowachonegi niya, “Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kwereu osechiwo jo-Juda e lwetu nikech nokecho kodgi, to un to koro usenegogi gi ich wangʼ marach omiyo wachni osetundo ira e polo.
\v 10 To koro udwaro keto chwo kod mond Juda gi Jerusalem wasumbiniu. Donge un bende un joketho kuom timo richo e nyim Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachu?
\v 11 Omiyo chikuru itu maber! Weuru joweteu ma usemako odogi nimar mirima mager osemako Jehova Nyasaye nikech un.”
\p 
\v 12 Eka jotelo moko mag Efraim kaka Azaria wuod Jehohanan gi Berekia wuod Meshilemoth gi Jehizkia wuod Shalum kod Amasa wuod Hadlai bende nodhi mokwero jogo mane oa e lweny.
\v 13 Negiwacho niya, “Ok unyal kelo jogo ma umako kaeni, nimar kutimo kamano to wanabed joketho e nyim Jehova Nyasaye. Koso udwaro medo richo ewi mago ma wasetimo? Richo ma wasetimo duongʼ moloyo kendo mirimbe mager ni kuom Israel.”
\p 
\v 14 Kuom mano, jolwenygi noweyo joma negimako kaachiel gi mwandu mane gipeyo ka gin e nyim jotelo kod joma nochokore duto.
\v 15 Joma noluong nying-gigo nokawo jogo mane omaki kendo negimiyo joma ne niduge duto lewni mane gigolo kuom gik mane gipeyo. Ne gimiyogi lewni kod wuoche, chiemo kod math, ne giwiro kuonde manoriemo gi mo. Jogo duto mane ool notingʼ e punde ka giterogi Jeriko, ma bende iluongo ni Dala Maduongʼ mar Othidhe kuma jowetegi mamoko ne nitiere, bangʼe negidok Samaria.
\p 
\v 16 E kindeno ruoth Ahaz nokwayo ruodh Asuria mondo okonye.
\v 17 Jo-Edom bende nomonjo jo-Juda kendo negimako ji mangʼeny.
\v 18 Jo-Filistia bende nosemonjo mier mane ni e bwo gode matindo kod man Negev ei Juda. Negimako kendo gikawo Beth Shemesh, Aijalon kod Gederoth kaachiel gi Soko, Timna kod Gimzo koriwore gi mier matindo molworogi.
\v 19 Jehova Nyasaye nodwoko jo-Juda chien nikech timbe Ahaz ruodh Israel nimar nosejiwo timbe maricho e piny Juda, kendo noseweyo luwo Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 20 Tiglath-Pilesa ruodh Asuria nobiro ire to kar konye to nomonje.
\v 21 Kuom mano, Ahaz nokawo gik moko mag hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye gi od ruoth kod ute joka ruoth momiyo ruodh Asuria to mano ne ok okonye.
\p 
\v 22 E ndalo mar chandruokne ruoth Ahaz nomedo weyo luwo Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 23 Notimo liswa ni nyiseche manono mag jo-Damaski mane oseloye. Noparo niya, “Nikech nyiseche manono mag ruodhi jo-Aram nokonyogi, abiro timo nigi liswa mondo mi gikonya.” To negimiyo opodho kaachiel gi jo-Israel.
\p 
\v 24 Ahaz nochoko gige lemo mag hekalu mar Nyasaye mogologi oko. Eka noloro dhout hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye bangʼe nogero kende mag misango e kamoro amora ma yore mag Jerusalem ogomoe.
\v 25 Nogero kuonde motingʼore gi malo mag lemo e miech Juda duto mondo otim misango ne nyiseche mamoko kokwinyogo Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kweregi mondo owangʼ iye.
\p 
\v 26 Gik mamoko duto mane otimo e ndalo lochne kod gik manotimo duto koa kar chakruokgi nyaka gikogi ondikie kitap ruodhi mag Juda kod Israel.
\v 27 Ahaz notho moyweyo gi kwerene kendo noyike e dala maduongʼ mar Jerusalem; to ne ok oike e liete ruodhi mag Israel. Kendo Hezekia wuode nobedo ruoth kare.
\c 29
\s1 Hezekia opwodho hekalu
\p 
\v 1 Hezekia ne ja-higni piero ariyo gabich kane obedo ruoth kendo norito piny kodak Jerusalem kuom higni piero ariyo gochiko. Min mare ne nyinge Abija nyar Zekaria.
\v 2 Notimo gima kare e nyim wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye mana kaka kwar mare Daudi notimo.
\p 
\v 3 E dwe mokwongo mar hik lochne mokwongo noyawo dhout hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye moloso.
\v 4 Noluongo jonabi kod jo-Lawi mondo ochokre e laru ma yo wuok chiengʼ.
\v 5 Kendo nowachonegi niya, “Winjauru un jo-Lawi! Koro pwodhreuru kendo chiwreuru ni hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kwereu. Goluru chilo maricho e kama ler mar lemo.
\v 6 Kwerewa ne ok jo-ratiro; omiyo negitimo richo e nyim wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachwa kane giweye. Ne gingʼanyone hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, ma giweyo luwe.
\v 7 Bende neginego teyni kendo loro dhout agola kendo ne ok giwangʼo ubani mangʼwe ngʼar kata chiwo misango miwangʼo pep e kama ler mar lemo mar Nyasach Israel.
\v 8 Omiyo mirima osemako Jehova Nyasaye gi jo-Juda kod Jerusalem; kendo nomiyo gibedo gima lich; miwuoro kendo mocha mana kaka uneno giwengeu uwegi.
\v 9 Mano emomiyo kwerewa noneg gi ligangla kendo yawuotwa gi nyiwa gi mondwa oter e twech.
\v 10 Koro adwaro timo singruok gi Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach jo-Israel mondo mi mirimbe mager owuog kuomwa.
\v 11 Un yawuota kik koro ujwangʼe, nikech Jehova Nyasaye oseyierou mondo uchungʼ e nyime kendo utine kuwangʼone ubani.”
\b
\li4 
\v 12 Eka jo-Lawi mane ochako tich ne gin:
\b
\li1 koa kuom joka Kohath,
\li2 Mahath wuod Amasai kod Joel wuod Azaria;
\li1 koa kuom Merari,
\li2 Kish wuod Abdi kod Azaria wuod Jehalelel;
\li1 koa kuom joka Gershon,
\li2 Joa wuod Zima kod Eden wuod Joa;
\li1 
\v 13 koa kuom nyikwa Elizafan,
\li2 Shimri gi Jeyel,
\li1 koa kuom nyikwa Asaf,
\li2 Zekaria kod Matania;
\li1 
\v 14 koa kuom nyikwa Heman,
\li2 Jehiel kod Shimei;
\li1 koa kuom nyikwa Jeduthun,
\li2 Shemaya kod Uziel.
\b
\p 
\v 15 Kane gisechoko owetegi mi gipwodhore eka negidonjo e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye mondo gipwodhe kaka ruoth nochiko kaluwore gi wach mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 16 Jodolo nodonjo e kama ler mar lemo mar Jehova Nyasaye mondo gipwodhe kendo negikelo e laru gimoro amora mochido mane ginwangʼo e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, eka jo-Lawi notingʼogi ka terogi oko nyaka e Holo mar Kidron.
\v 17 Negichako tich pwodho hekalu chiengʼ mokwongo mar dwe mokwongo to chiengʼ mar aboro mar dweno negichopo e agola mar Jehova Nyasaye. To kuom ndalo aboro mamoko ne gipwodho hekaluno mar Jehova Nyasaye kendo ne gitieke chiengʼ mar apar gauchiel mar dweno.
\p 
\v 18 Bangʼe negidhi ir ruoth Hezekia kagiwachone niya, “Wasepwodho hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye duto kaachiel gi kendo mar misango miwangʼo pep gi gik moko duto mitiyogo e kendono kod mesa makati mopwodhi kod gigene duto.
\v 19 Waseloso kendo pwodho gik moko duto mane ruoth Ahaz ne ogolo oko nikech noweyo luwo Nyasaye kane en ruoth, kendo oseketgi e nyim kendo mar misango miwangʼo mar Jehova Nyasaye.”
\p 
\v 20 Kinyne gokinyi ruoth Hezekia nochoko jodongo mag dala maduongʼ kaachiel kendo negidhi e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 21 Negikelo rwedhi abiriyo, gi imbe abiriyo gi nyirombe abiriyo kod nywogi abiriyo mondo gichiw kaka misango mar golo richo mar pinyruoth, gi mar kama ler mar lemo kod Juda. Ruoth nochiko jodolo ma nyikwa Harun mondo gichiw gigo e kendo mar misango mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 22 Omiyo noyangʼ rwedhigo mi jodolo nokawo remo mokiro e kendo mar misango, bangʼe ne giyangʼo imbe mine gikawo remo ma gikiro e kendo mar misango.
\v 23 Eka nokel nywogi mag misango mar golo richo e nyim ruoth kod joma nochokore mine giyieyo lwetgi kuomgi.
\v 24 Bangʼe jodolo noyangʼogi mi gichiwo rembgi e kendo mar misango kaka misango mar golo richo mondo ochulgo richo mar jo-Israel duto nikech ruoth nochiko mondo ochiw misango miwangʼo pep kod misango mar golo richo ne jo-Israel duto.
\p 
\v 25 Noketo jo-Lawi e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye momiyogi ongengʼo, gi nyatiti kod orutu kaluwore gi chik Daudi gi mar Gad janen mar ruoth kod mar Nathan janabi. Chikni nogol kod jonabi kowuok kuom Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 26 Omiyo jo-Lawi nochungʼ koikore gi thumbe mag Daudi to jodolo noikore kod turumbete.
\p 
\v 27 Hezekia nochiko mondo otim misango miwangʼo pep e kendo mar misango. Kane chiwo misango ochakore, wer ne Jehova Nyasaye bende nochakore ka gigoyo turumbete kod thumbe mag Daudi ruodh Israel.
\v 28 Joma nochokore duto nokulore piny ka gilemo ka jower wer to jogo turumbete goyo turumbete. Mano nodhi nyime nyaka notiek chiwo misango miwangʼo pep.
\p 
\v 29 Kane otiek chiwo misango ruoth kod jogo duto mane ni kode nogoyo chonggi piny ka gimiye duongʼ.
\v 30 Ruoth Hezekia gi jodonge nochiko jo-Lawi mondo opak Jehova Nyasaye gi wende mag Daudi kod Asaf janen. Omiyo ne giwero wende pak ka gimor kendo ka gimiye duongʼ.
\p 
\v 31 Eka Hezekia nowacho niya, “Koro usechiworu ne Jehova Nyasaye, biuru mondo ukel misengni kod chiwo mag erokamano e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.” Omiyo joma nochokore nokelo misengini kod chiwo mag goyo erokamano kendo jogo duto ma chunygi ne oyie nokelo misango miwangʼo pep.
\p 
\v 32 Kar romb misengini miwangʼo pep mane joma ochokore nokelo ne gin rwedhi piero abiriyo, kod imbe mia achiel gi nyiimbe mia ariyo magi duto nochiw kaka misango miwangʼo pep ni Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 33 To jamni mane owal mondo otimgo misengini ni ruoth ne gin rwedhi mia auchiel kod rombe gi diek alufu adek.
\v 34 Kata kamano jodolo ne nok ahinya mane ok nyal yangʼo chiayo mar misango miwangʼo pep; omiyo jowetegi ma jo-Lawi nokonyogi nyaka negitieko tich kendo nyaka jodolo moko notieko pwodhore, nimar jo-Lawi ne jokinda kuom pwodhruokgi moloyo jodolo.
\v 35 Misengini miwangʼo pep ne ngʼeny moloyo kaachiel gi boche miwangʼo mar lalruok kod misango miolo piny mane ochiw kaachiel gi misango miwangʼo pep.
\p Kamano e kaka lemo mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye nodwok kare.
\v 36 Hezekia kod ji duto nobedo mamor kod gima Nyasaye notimone joge, nikech notimo mapiyo.
\c 30
\s1 Hezekia otimo Sap Pasaka
\p 
\v 1 Hezekia nooro wach ni jo-Israel duto gi jo-Juda kendo nondiko barupe ni jo-Efraim kod jo-Manase kokwayogi mondo gibi Jerusalem e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye mondo gitim Sap Pasaka ni Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach jo-Israel.
\v 2 Ruoth gi jodonge kod joma nochokore Jerusalem nowinjore ni gitim Sap Pasaka e dwe mar ariyo.
\v 3 Ne ok ginyal time e kinde mane onego otime nimar jodolo moromo ne pok opwodhore to ji bende ne pok ochokore Jerusalem.
\v 4 Chenroni ne berne ruoth kod joma nochokore.
\v 5 Negingʼado bura mondo giland wachni e Israel duto kochakore Bersheba nyaka Dan kagiluongo ji mondo gibi Jerusalem otim Pasaka mar Jehova Nyasaye Nyasach Israel nikech ne pok otime gi ji mangʼeny kaka ondiki.
\p 
\v 6 Omiyo joote nodhi Israel gi Juda duto kaka ruoth nochiko ka gitingʼo barupe mane oa ir ruoth kod jodonge mondikie niya,
\pm “Jo-Israel dwoguru ir Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach Ibrahim gi Isaka kod Israel mondo mi oduog iru un joma odongʼ mosetony e lwet ruodhi mag Asuria.
\v 7 Kik ubed ka kwereu gi oweteu mane oweyo luwo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kwereu momiyo gidoko gima iluoro mana kaka uneno sani.
\v 8 Kik ubed gi tok matek kaka kwereu nobedo, bolreuru ni Jehova Nyasaye. Biuru e kama ler mar lemo ma osepwodho nyaka chiengʼ. Tineuru Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachu mondo mi mirimbe mager owuog kuomu.
\v 9 Ka udwogo ir Jehova Nyasaye eka joweteu gi nyithindu notimnegi ngʼwono mi nowegi giduogi e pinygi kod joma noterogi e twech nikech Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachu en jangʼwono kendo en gihera maduongʼ omiyo ok noloknu ngʼeye ka udwogo ire.”
\p 
\v 10 Joote nodhi e dala ka dala e piny Efraim gi Manase duto nyaka ochopo Zebulun to ji nocharogi kendo nyierogi.
\v 11 To kata kamano jo-Asher moko kod jo-Manase kaachiel gi jo-Zebulun nobolore modhi Jerusalem.
\v 12 To e piny Juda bende ema ne lwet Nyasaye ne nitie kuom jogo mondo omigi bedo e paro achiel mondo gitim gima ruoth gi jodonge nochiko kaluwore gi wach mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 13 Ji mangʼeny nochokore Jerusalem e dwe mar ariyo mondo gitim Sap Makati ma ok oketie Thowi.
\v 14 Negigolo kende mag misango miwangʼoe liswa mane nitie Jerusalem kaachiel gi kende mag misango miwangʼoe ubani mi giwitogi e Holo mar Kidron.
\p 
\v 15 Ne giyangʼo nyarombo mar Pasaka Chiengʼ mar apar gangʼwen mar dwe mar ariyo jodolo kod jo-Lawi noyudo wichkuot omiyo negipwodhore mi gikelo misengini miwangʼo pep e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 16 Bangʼe negikawo keregi mapile kaka ondikie chike Musa ngʼat Nyasaye. Jodolo nokiro remo manomigi kod jo-Lawi.
\v 17 Nikech ji mangʼeny ei oganda ne pod ok opwodhore, nochuno jo-Lawi mondo oyangʼ nyirombe mag Sap Pasaka ni jogo duto mane ok ler kendo ne ok nyal chiwo nyirombegi ni Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 18 Kata obedo ni ji mathoth manowuok e piny Efraim gi Manase gi Isakar kod Zebulun ne ok opwodhore, to kata kamano negichamo Pasaka ka ok giluwo gima nondiki. To Hezekia nolamonigi kawacho niya, “Mad Jehova Nyasaye mangʼwon owene ngʼato angʼata,
\v 19 moseketo chunye mondo oluw Nyasaye ma en Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kwerene kata obedo ni ok oler kaluwore gi chike mag kama ler mar lemo.”
\v 20 Omiyo Jehova Nyasaye nowinjo kwayo mar Hezekia mochango jogo.
\p 
\v 21 Jo-Israel mane nitiere Jerusalem notimo Sap Makati ma ok oketie Thowi kuom ndalo abiriyo ka gimor gi-ilo maduongʼ ka jo-Lawi kod jodolo werne Jehova Nyasaye pile ka pile ka gigoyo thumbe mag pak mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 22 Hezekia nojiwo jo-Lawi duto mane ongʼeyo tich mar tiyo ne Jehova Nyasaye. Kuom ndalo abiriyo negichamo chiemo mane opognigi kendo negitimo misango mar lalruok kagipako Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach kweregi.
\p 
\v 23 Jogo mane ochokore nowinjore mondo gimed timo sawoni ndalo abiriyo mamoko, omiyo kuom ndalo abiriyo mamoko negitimo kamano gi mor.
\v 24 Hezekia ruodh Juda nochiwo ni joma nochokore rwedhi alufu achiel kod rombe gi diek alufu abiriyo, to jodonge nochiwonegi rwedhi alufu achiel kod rombe gi diek alufu apar. Jodolo mangʼeny ahinya nopwodhore.
\v 25 Joma nochokore duto mane oa Juda kaachiel gi jodolo kod jo-Lawi kod joma nochokore koa Israel kaachiel gi jodak mane odak Israel kod mane odak Juda ne mor gi ilo.
\v 26 Ne nitie mor maduongʼ Jerusalem mapok nobedo Jerusalem chakre ndalo Solomon wuod Daudi ma ruodh Israel.
\v 27 Jodolo gi jo-Lawi nochungʼ mondo ogwedh ji, kendo Nyasaye nowinjogi nikech lembgi nochopo e polo kar dakne maler.
\c 31
\p 
\v 1 Kane magi duto oserumo, jo-Israel duto mane ni kanyo nodhi e miech Juda ma gitoyo kite milamo kendo negingʼado sirni milamo mag Ashera. Negimuko kuonde motingʼore malo mag lemo kaachiel gi kende mag misango miwangʼoe liswa e piny Juda gi Benjamin kod piny Efraim gi Manase. Bangʼe kane gisemukogi duto, jo-Israel nodok kuondegi mag dak e miechgi.
\s1 Chiwruok ne lemo
\p 
\v 2 Hezekia nopogo jodolo kod jo-Lawi migepe mondo gichiw misengini miwangʼo pep kod misango mar lalruok kod tije lemo gi dwoko erokamano kod wero wende pak e dhorangeye mag kambi Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 3 Ruoth nochiwore koa kuom mwandune gik mitimogo misengini miwangʼo pep mag chiengʼ Sabato gi mag chiengʼ dwe manyien kendo ndalo mag sewni moyier kaka ondiki e Chik Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 4 Nochiko joma nodak Jerusalem mondo ochiw ni jodolo gi jo-Lawi pokgi mondo mi gichiwre gi chunygi duto ne Chik mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 5 Mapiyo nono ka wachni nochopo ni ji, jo-Israel nochiwo cham magikwongo kayo, gi divai magikwongo loso gi mor Zeituni mokwongo nyak gi mor kich kod gik moko duto mag puodho.
\v 6 Jo-Israel kod jo-Juda mane odak e dalane mag Juda bende nokelo achiel kuom apar mag dhok gi jamni kaachiel gi achiel kuom apar mar gik maler mane gichiwone Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachgi kendo nochokgi e pidhe.
\v 7 Negichako dhuro pidhego chakre dwe mar adek kendo negitieko dhurogi e dwe mar abiriyo.
\v 8 Kane Hezekia gi jodonge nobiro moneno pidhego negipako Jehova Nyasaye kendo negigwedho jo-Israel.
\p 
\v 9 Hezekia nopenjo jodolo kod jo-Lawi wach pidhego,
\v 10 eka Azaria jadolo maduongʼ ma anywola Zadok nodwoke niya, “Nyaka ji chak kelo chiemo e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, wasechiemo mawayiengʼ kendo chiemo mangʼeny pod odongʼ nikech Jehova Nyasaye osegwedho joge, mano emomiyo magi odongʼ.”
\p 
\v 11 Hezekia nochiko mondo oik kuonde keno mag hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye mi notim kamano.
\v 12 Bangʼe negikelo gadiera chiwo gi achiel kuom apar kod mich mowal. Konania ja-Lawi ne jarit mar gigo to jatelo maluwe ne owadgi Shimei.
\v 13 Jehiel, Azazia, Nahath, Asahel, Jerimoth, Jozabad, Eliel, Ismakia, Mahath kod Benaya ne jotelo e bwo Konania kod Shimei owadgi. Jogi duto notiyo kaluwore gi tich mane ruoth Hezekia kod Azaria mane jatelo morito hekalu mar Nyasaye omiyogi.
\p 
\v 14 Kore wuod Imna ma ja-Lawi, jarit rangach ma yo wuok chiengʼ, ne jarit chiwo mar hera, ka opogo gik mochiwne Jehova Nyasaye kod chiwo mowal.
\v 15 Eden, Miniamin, Jeshua, Shemaya, Amaria kod Shekania ne okonye gadiera ka gidak e miech jodolo, ka gipogo jodolo wetegi kaluwore gi migepegi, jomadongo gi jomatindo machal.
\p 
\v 16 Bende ne gipogone chwo mahikgi adek kadhi nyime mane nying-gi ondiki e nonro margi mar anywola, jogo duto mane nyalo donjo e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye mondo gitim tijegi mapile mopogore opogore kaluwore gi tich manomigi kaachiel gi migepegi.
\v 17 Kendo ne gipogone jodolo mane ondik nying-gi kaluwore gi ndiko mar chenro mar nonro mar anywolagi kendo jo-Lawi ma jo-higni piero ariyo kadhi nyime bende notimnigi kamano kaluwore gi tije mag-gi kod migepegi.
\v 18 Magi notingʼo jomatindo duto gi mon gi yawuowi kod nyiri duto mag dhoodno kaka ondikgi e nonro mar anywolagi. Negitimo gima nikare kuom pwodhruokgi.
\p 
\v 19 To jonabi mane nyikwa Harun mane odak e puothe mipuro molworo miechgi kata mane odak e mier mamoko ne oyier joma ne pogo gik moko ne ngʼato angʼata mane nitie e diergi ma dichwo kaachiel gi jogo duto mane ondik nying-gi koa e dhood Lawi.
\p 
\v 20 Magi e gik mane Hezekia otimo e piny Juda duto kotimo maber kendo makare kendo mowinjore ni Jehova Nyasaye ma ok obagni.
\v 21 Gimoro amora mane otimo ei hekalu mar Nyasaye kaluwore gi bura kod chike, notimo komanyo Nyasache gi chunye duto. Omiyo nogwedhe.
\c 32
\s1 Senakerib obwogo Jerusalem
\p 
\v 1 Bangʼ tich maber mane Hezekia otimo, Senakerib ruodh Asuria nobiro momonjo Juda. Ne ogoyo agengʼa ne mier mochiel gohinga koparo ni onyalo kawogi mondo gidok mage.
\v 2 Kane Hezekia oneno ni Senakerib nosebiro kendo noparo mar kedo kod Jerusalem,
\v 3 noporo wach gi jodonge kod jotend lweny mondo gigengʼ pi soko moa oko mar dala maduongʼ kendo ne gikonye.
\v 4 Oganda maduongʼ nochokore kendo ne gigengʼo sokni duto aore mane kadho e piny kagiwacho niya, “Angʼo momiyo ruodhi mag Asuria biro mondo onwangʼ pi mangʼeny.”
\v 5 Eka notiyo matek koloso kuonde mane omukore mag ohinga kendo nogero kuonde maboyo mag ngʼicho. Nogero ohinga machielo e tok mokwongo kendo nomedo loso ndiri mosiro Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi. Bende noloso gig lweny kod okumbni mangʼeny.
\p 
\v 6 Noketo jotend lweny mondo otel ne ji kendo nochokogi e nyime e laru mar dhoranga dala maduongʼ kendo nojiwogi gi wechegi:
\v 7 “Beduru motegno kendo gi chir. Kik ubed gi luoro kata kik chunyu tho nikech ruodh Asuria kod jolweny mangʼeny man kode nimar wan gi teko maduongʼ moloye.
\v 8 Teko mar dhano ema ni kode to wan to wan kod Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa makonyowa kendo kedonwa e lwenjewa.” Kendo ji nobedo gi chir kane giwinjo wach Hezekia ruodh Juda.
\p 
\v 9 Bangʼe kane Senakerib ruodh Asuria kod jolweny mage duto ne ogoyo agengʼa Lakish, nooro jotend lweny mage Jerusalem mondo owach ne Hezekia ruodh Juda kod jo-Juda duto mane ni kanyo kowacho niya,
\pm 
\v 10 “Ma e gima Senakerib ruodh Asuria wacho: En kama nade miketoe genoni, momiyo isiko Jerusalem ka ogoni agengʼa?
\v 11 Ka Hezekia wacho ni, ‘Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachwa biro resowa e lwet ruodh Asuria,’ donge uparo ni owitou mondo kech gi riyo onegu?
\v 12 Donge Hezekia owuon nomuko kuonde motingʼore mar lemo kod kende mag misango mag nyasayeni kowachone jo-Juda kod jo-Jerusalem ni, ‘Nyaka ulam e nyim kendo mar misango achiel kendo unuwangʼ misango mau e wiye’?
\pm 
\v 13 “Donge ungʼeyo gima an kod kwerena osetimo ni ogendini mamoko duto mag pinje? Dak ne nyiseche pinjego duto resgi e lweta?
\v 14 Kuom nyiseche duto mag ogendini mane kwerena otieko, en mane kuomgi mosereso joge e lweta? Angʼo momiyo uparo ni nyasachu biro resou e lweta?
\v 15 Omiyo kik uwe Hezekia wuondu kendo mi ulal kama. Kik uyie kode nikech onge nyasach oganda kata pinyruoth moro amora ma osereso joge e lweta kata e lwet kwerena. Omiyo ere kaka nyasachu noresu e lweta!”
\p 
\v 16 Jotelo mag Senakerib nomedo wuoyo marach kuom Jehova Nyasaye kendo kuom jatichne Hezekia.
\v 17 Bende ruoth nondiko baruwa moyanyogo Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel kendo nowuoyo kuome kojare niya, “Mana kaka nyiseche mag jopinje moko ne ok oresogi e lweta, omiyo nyasach Hezekia bende ok nores joge e lweta.”
\v 18 Bangʼe negiluongo joma ne nitie Jerusalem e ohinga ka gikok gi dwol maduongʼ gi dho jo-Hibrania mondo obwog-gi kendo omi gibed gi luoro eka mondo gikaw dala maduongʼno.
\v 19 Ne giwuoyo marach kuom Nyasach Jerusalem kaka ne giwuoyo kuom nyiseche molos gi lwedo mag ogendini mag piny.
\p 
\v 20 Ruoth Hezekia gi janabi Isaya wuod Amoz noywagore ka lemo e nyim polo kuom wachni.
\v 21 Omiyo Jehova Nyasaye nooro malaika mane onego jolweny gi jochungʼ kod jotelo e kambi mar ruodh Asuria, omiyo nowuok modok e pinye gi wichkuot. Kane odhi e kar lemo mar nyasache, yawuote moko nonege kod ligangla.
\p 
\v 22 Kamano e kaka Jehova Nyasaye noreso Hezekia kod jo-Jerusalem motony e lwet Senakerib ruodh Asuria kendo e lwet ruodhi mamoko bende. Omiyo Jehova Nyasaye noritogi kuom pinje duto mane olworogi.
\v 23 Ji mangʼeny nokelo ni Jehova Nyasaye mich mag-gi Jerusalem kendo Hezekia ruodh Juda bende negikelone mich ma nengogi tek, kendo chakre kanyo ogendini duto nomiye luor maduongʼ.
\s1 Sunga, tich maber kod tho mar Hezekia
\p 
\v 24 E ndalogo Hezekia nobedo matuo kendo nohewore, omiyo nolamo Jehova Nyasaye mane odwoke kendo nomiye ranyisi mar hono.
\v 25 To Hezekia ne nigi sunga e chunye kendo ne ok odwoko erokamano kaluwore gi ngʼwono manotimne; omiyo mirima nomako Jehova Nyasaye kode kaachiel gi Juda gi Jerusalem.
\v 26 To Hezekia nolokore moweyo timo richo mar sungruok e chunye mana kaka jo-Jerusalem bende notimo, omiyo mirimb Jehova Nyasaye ne ok ochako omake kodgi e ndalo Hezekia.
\p 
\v 27 Hezekia ne nigi mwandu mangʼeny kod luor mi noloso kuondege mag fedha gi dhahabu gi kite ma nengogi tek gi gik mangʼwe ngʼar, gi okumbni kod gik moko mopogore opogore mabeyo mage.
\v 28 Bende nogoyo deche mikane cham mokaa gi divai molos manyien kod mo kendo nogero kunde ne dhok mopogore opogore kod abila mag rombe.
\v 29 Nogero mier kendo ne en kod rombe mangʼeny kod kweth mag dhok nikech Nyasaye nogwedhe kod mwandu mangʼeny.
\p 
\v 30 Hezekia ema ne ogengʼo thidhna matin mar Gihon kobaro pige mondo oluw bath Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi yo podho chiengʼ. Tije duto mane lwete omulo nodhi maber.
\v 31 To kane oorne joote gi jotend Babulon mondo openje kuom ranyisi mar hono mane otimore e piny, Nyasaye noweye mondo oteme mondo eka ongʼe gima ne nitiere e chunye.
\p 
\v 32 Weche mamoko duto mag ndalo loch Hezekia kod timbene mabeyo ondiki e fweny mar janabi Isaya wuod Amoz e kitap ruodhi mag Juda kod Israel.
\v 33 Hezekia notho moyweyo kaka kwerene kendo noyike e got kama liete nyikwa Daudi ne nitiere. Jo-Juda duto kod joma ne nitie Jerusalem nomiye duongʼ kane otho kendo Manase wuode nobedo ruoth kare.
\c 33
\s1 Manase ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 1 Manase ne ja-higni apar gariyo kane odoko ruoth kendo nobedo e loch kuom higni piero abich gabich kodak Jerusalem.
\v 2 Notimo richo e nyim wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye koluwo timbe mamono mag ogendini mane Jehova Nyasaye oseriembo e dier jo-Israel.
\v 3 Ne ochako ogero kuonde motingʼore gi malo mag lemo ma wuon mare Hezekia nomuko, to bende nogero kende mag misengini miwangʼoe liswa ne Baal kaachiel gi sirni milamo mag Ashera. Bende nokulore kolamo gik moko duto mochwe man e kor polo.
\v 4 Ne ogero kende mag misengini e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kata obedo ni Jehova Nyasaye nosewacho niya, “Nyinga nobed Jerusalem nyaka chiengʼ.”
\v 5 Nogero kende mag misengini miwangʼoe liswa ne gik mochwe mae kor polo e laru ariyo mag hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 6 Notimo misango kochiwo nyithinde mondo owangʼ e mach e Holo mar Ben Hinom bende noiro ji kendo nogoyo gagi gi timo timbe jwok, kendo nopenjo josepe kod jo-nyakalondo. Notimo timbe maricho mangʼeny e nyim Jehova Nyasaye, omiyo Jehova Nyasaye nokecho.
\p 
\v 7 Nokawo kido mopa mane oloso moketo e hekalu mar Nyasaye mane oyudo Nyasaye osewuoyoe ne Daudi kod wuode Solomon niya, “Aseyiero hekaluni gi Jerusalem e kind ogendini duto mag Israel, kendo abiro keto Nyinga kanyo nyaka chiengʼ.
\v 8 Ka jo-Israel orito chike duto kendo otimo gik moko duto mane achikogi, kendo oluwo buche gi chike duto mane Musa onyisogi, to ok nariembgi e piny mane amiyo kweregi.”
\v 9 Kata kamano Manase nomiyo jo-Juda kod jo-Jerusalem oweyo Jehova Nyasaye mi gimedo timo timbe maricho moloyo ogendini mane Jehova Nyasaye otieko e nyim jo-Israel.
\p 
\v 10 Jehova Nyasaye nowuoyo kod Manase gi joge to ne ok gidewe.
\v 11 Omiyo Jehova Nyasaye nokelonigi jotend jolweny mag ruodh Asuria momako Manase otero e twech kotuch ume kod olowu kendo otweye kod rateke mag mula motere Babulon.
\v 12 Koro e thagruokne nokwayo ngʼwono kuom Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasache kobolore ahinya e nyim Nyasach kwerene.
\v 13 Kane okwayo, Jehova Nyasaye noneno bolruokne mowinjo ywakne omiyo nodwoge Jerusalem e pinyruodhe; bangʼe Manase nongʼeyo ni Jehova Nyasaye en Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 14 Bangʼe nogero ohinga ma oko mar Dala Maduongʼ mar Daudi yo podho chiengʼ mar aora Gihon manie holo nyaka ochopo kar donjo mar Ranga Rech kendo nolworo got Ofel mogere modhi malo ahinya. Noketo jotend lweny e mier madongo duto mag Juda mochiel motegno gi ohinga.
\p 
\v 15 Nogolo nyiseche manono ma welo kod kido mar nyasaye manono mane ni e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kaachiel gi kende mag misango miwangʼoe liswa duto mane ogero e got mar hekalu kod Jerusalem kendo nowitogi oko mar dala maduongʼ.
\v 16 Bangʼe nochako ogero kendo mar misango mar Jehova Nyasaye kendo notimo misango mar lalruok kod chiwo mag erokamano kuome kowachone Juda mondo otine Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach jo-Israel.
\v 17 Kata kamano, ji nodhi nyime kod timo misengini e kuonde motingʼore malo mag lemo to negitime ne Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachgi kende.
\p 
\v 18 Weche mag ndalo loch Manase kaachiel gi kwayo mane okwayogo Nyasache, kod weche mane jonen nowachone kuom nying Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach jo-Israel ondiki e kitepe mag ruodhi Israel.
\v 19 Lemo mare kod kaka Nyasaye nowinjo ywakne kaachiel gi richone kod kethone duto kod kuonde manogeroe kuonde motingʼore malo mag lemo kaachiel gi sirni mag Ashera milamo, kod nyiseche manono kapod ok olokore, magi duto ondiki e kitap jonen.
\v 20 Manase notho kaka kwerene kendo noyike e ode mar ruoth. Amon wuode nobedo ruoth kare.
\s1 Amon ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 21 Amon ne ja-higni piero ariyo gariyo kane obedo ruoth kendo norito piny kodak Jerusalem kuom higni ariyo.
\v 22 Notimo timbe maricho e wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye mana kaka wuon mare Manase nosetimo. Amon nolamo kendo timo liswa ne nyiseche duto manono mane Manase oseloso.
\v 23 To kopogore gi wuon mare ma Manase ne ok obolore e nyim Jehova Nyasaye nikech nomedo timo gik maricho.
\p 
\v 24 Jodongo mag Amon nowinjore monego ruoth e kar dakne.
\v 25 Eka jopinyno noriwore monego jogo duto mane onego ruoth Amon kendo negiketo Josia wuode obedo ruoth kare.
\c 34
\s1 Tij Josia maber
\p 
\v 1 Josia ne ja-higni aboro kane obedo ruoth kendo norito pinyno kodak Jerusalem kuom higni piero adek gachiel.
\v 2 Timbe Josia ne longʼo e wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye kendo nowuotho e yore duto mag Daudi kwar-gi ma ok olokore kongʼiyo korachwich kata koracham.
\p 
\v 3 E higa mar aboro mar lochne kane pod en rawera nochako luwo Nyasach Daudi kwar mare. E hike mar apar gariyo nochako pwodho Juda kod Jerusalem koketho kuonde motingʼore gi malo mag lemo, gi sirni mag lemo mar Ashera, gi nyiseche mopa kod kido mothedhi.
\v 4 Kaluwore kod chik mane ogolo, kende liswa mag Baal nomuki; nomuko kende mag misango miwangʼoe ubani mane ochungʼ e wigi motoyogi matindo tindo, kendo nomuko sirni mag Ashera milamo, nyiseche manono kod kido milamo mongʼadogi matindo tindo. Magi nongʼinjo matindo tindo mokeyogi ewi liete mag jogo mane otimonegi liswa.
\v 5 Nowangʼo choke jodolo e kendegi mag misango omiyo nopwodho Juda kod Jerusalem.
\v 6 Kamano bende e miech Manase gi Efraim kod Simeon nyaka chop Naftali kaachiel gi kuonde molworogi mane osekethi,
\v 7 nomuko kende mag misango gi sirni mag Ashera milamo kendo notoyo nyisechegi mongʼinyore ka buru kendo nongʼado matindo tindo kende miwangʼoe ubani e piny Israel duto, bangʼe noduogo Jerusalem.
\p 
\v 8 E higa mar apar gaboro mar loch Josia mondo neni opwodh piny kod hekalu nooro Shafan wuod Azalia gi Maseya jatend dala maduongʼ kaachiel gi Joa wuod Joahaz ma jachan weche mondo olos hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache.
\p 
\v 9 Negidhi ir Hilkia jadolo maduongʼ mi gimiye pesa mane osekel e hekalu mar Nyasaye ma jo-Lawi ma jorit dhoudi nosechoko kuom jo-Manase gi jo-Efraim kod jo-Israel duto mane odongʼ gi jo-Juda gi jo-Benjamin kaachiel gi joma nodak Jerusalem.
\v 10 Negiketogi e lwet joma otelo ne gedo mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye. Jogi nochulo jotich mane oloso kendo odwogo hekalu kaka ne ochalo chon.
\v 11 Jopa bepe kod jogedo bende nomi pesa mondo gingʼiewgo kite mopa kod yiend ripo kod sirni mondo gilosgo udi mane ruodhi Juda oweyo okethore.
\p 
\v 12 Jogo ne otiyo tijno gadiera. E tijno notelnigi kod jo-Lawi mane gin Jahath kod Obadia mane gin nyikwa Merari, kendo Zekaria gi Meshulam mane nyikwa Kohath. Jo-Lawi, ma gin jogo duto mane olony kuom goyo thumbe
\v 13 ema notelo ne jotich kendo negingʼiyo jotich mag tije mopogore opogore. Jo-Lawi moko ne jogoro gi jopuonj chike kod jorit dhoudi.
\s1 Kitap Chik oyudi
\p 
\v 14 Kane gigolo oko pesa mane oseter e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, Hilkia jadolo nonwangʼo Kitap Chik mar Jehova Nyasaye mane ochiw ne Musa.
\v 15 Hilkia nowachone Shafan jagoro niya, “Aseyudo Kitap Chik ei hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.” Nochiwe ni Shafan.
\p 
\v 16 Eka Shafan nokawo kitabuno motere ni ruoth mowachone niya, “Jodongi tiyo tije duto mane osemigi.
\v 17 Gisechulo pesa mane nitiere e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kendo gisechiwogi e lwet jotich kod jotend hekalu.”
\v 18 Bangʼe Shafan jagoro nowachone niya, “Hilkia jadolo osemiya kitabu moro.” Mi Shafan nosomo kitabuno e nyim ruoth.
\p 
\v 19 Kane ruoth owinjo weche mag Chik, noyiecho lepe.
\v 20 Nochiwo chikegi ne Hilkia gi Ahikam wuod Shafan gi Abdon wuod Mika gi Shafan jagoro kod Asaya jarit mar ruoth kowachonegi niya,
\v 21 “Dhiuru upenj Jehova Nyasaye gima biro timorena, jo-Israel kod jo-Juda modongʼ kaluwore gi weche mantiere e kitabu mosenwangʼno. Mirimb Jehova Nyasaye maliel ka mach osechomowa nikech kwerewa ok oserito wach Jehova Nyasaye; kendo ok gisetimo timbe moluwore gi gik moko duto mondiki e kitabuni.”
\p 
\v 22 Hilkia gi jogo mane ruoth ooro kaachiel kode nodhi ir Hulda janabi madhako mane chi Shalum wuod Tokhath, ma wuod Hasra jarit kar keno mar lep lemo. Nodak Jerusalem e gwengʼ mar ariyo.
\p 
\v 23 Hulda jadolo madhako nowachonegi niya, “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach jo-Israel wacho: Nyisuru ngʼatno mane oorou ira niya,
\v 24 ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Abiro kelo masira e pinyni kendo kuom joma odakie, kaluwore gi kwongʼ duto mondikie kitabu mosesom e nyim ruodh Juda.
\v 25 Mirimba nosik kuom pinyni kendo ok norum nikech gisejwangʼa ka giwangʼo ubani ne nyiseche manono kendo ka gimiya mirima kuom lamo nyiseche mopa gi lwedo.’
\v 26 Wachneuru ruodh Juda, mane oorou mondo upenja gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach jo-Israel wacho kaluwore gi weche musewinjo:
\v 27 Nikech ne uwinjo wach kendo uboloru e nyim Nyasaye kane uwinjo weche mane owacho kuom pinyni kod joma odakie, kendo nikech ne uboloru e nyima, ma uyiecho lepu kuywak e nyima, omiyo asewinjo ywaku, Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\v 28 Koro anami iywe gi kwereni kendo noiki gi kwe. Ok inine masiche mabiro kelone pinyni gi joma odakie.’ ”
\p Omiyo negidwoko wach ne ruoth.
\p 
\v 29 Eka ruoth noluongo jodongo duto mag Juda kod Jerusalem kaachiel.
\v 30 Nodhi nyaka e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye ka en gi jo-Juda, jo-Jerusalem, jodolo, jo-Lawi, kaachiel gi ji duto momewo kod ma jochan. Nosomonegi weche duto mane ondiki e Kitabu mar Singruok mane osenwangʼ e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye ka giwinjo.
\v 31 Ruoth nochungʼ e bath siro kendo noketo winjruok mane oselal obedo kare e nyim Jehova Nyasaye kosingore ni enoluw Jehova Nyasaye kendo norit chikene gi wechene kod buchene gi chunye duto kod pache duto kendo norit weche mag singruok mondiki e kitabuni.
\p 
\v 32 Eka nomiyo jo-Jerusalem duto kod jo-Benjamin okwongʼore ni ginirit singruokno kendo jo-Jerusalem notimo mano kaluwore gi singruok mar Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kweregi.
\p 
\v 33 Josia nogolo gik makwero mag nyiseche manono e piny jo-Israel duto kendo nomiyo ji duto modak e piny Israel otiyo ne Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachgi. E ndalo duto mag ngimane ji ne ok oweyo luwo Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kweregi.
\c 35
\s1 Josia otimo Sap Pasaka
\p 
\v 1 Josia notimo Sap Pasaka ni Jehova Nyasaye e Jerusalem kendo ne oneg nyarombo mar Pasaka chiengʼ mar apar gangʼwen mar dwe mokwongo.
\v 2 Noketo jodolo e tijegi kendo nojiwogi kuom tich hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 3 Nowachone jo-Lawi mane osepwodhi ni Jehova Nyasaye mondo opuonj jo-Israel duto niya, “Keturu Sanduku Maler e hekalu mane Solomon wuod Daudi ruodh Israel nogero. Ok onego utingʼe e goku. Omiyo tineuru Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachu kendo ni joge Israel.
\v 4 Chanreuru e migepe kaluwore gi anywolau kaka chik mane Daudi ruodh jo-Israel kod Solomon wuode ondiko.
\p 
\v 5 “Chunguru Kama Ler gi jo-Lawi moko e kind migepe matindo mag anywola mar joweteu mamoko.
\v 6 Yangʼuru nyiromb Pasaka kendo pwodhreuru mondo ukony joweteu timo gima Jehova Nyasaye nochiko gi dho Musa mondo utim.”
\p 
\v 7 Eka Josia nochiwo ni joma nochokore nyirombe gi diek moromo alufu piero adek kod rwedhi alufu adek mondo otimgo misango mar Pasaka. Magi duto nochiwo kogolo kuom mwandune owuon.
\p 
\v 8 Jodonge bende nokelo chiwo kuom herogi ni ji gi jodolo kod jo-Lawi. Hilkia gi Zekaria kod Jehiel ma jotelo madongo mag hekalu mar Nyasaye nochiwo ni jodolo nyirombe kod diek alufu ariyo gi mia auchiel kod dhok mia adek mondo otimgo misango mar Pasaka.
\v 9 Konania bende, kaachiel gi Shemaya kod Nethanel ma owetene kod Hashabia gi Jeyel kod Jozabad mane jatend jo-Lawi nomiyo jo-Lawi nyirombe kod diek alufu abich kod dhok mia abich mondo otimgo misango mar Pasaka.
\p 
\v 10 Kane gige tich duto oseikore, jodolo nochungʼ keregi kendo jo-Lawi nobedo e migepegi kaka ne ruoth osechiko.
\v 11 Nyirombe mag Pasaka nochinji kendo jo-Lawi nomiyo jodolo remo kapod giyangʼo chiayogo mi jodolo nokiro remogo.
\v 12 Negiwalo mago mane mag misengini miwangʼo pep ma gimiyo migepe matindo tindo mag ariyo mar anywola mar ji mondo gichiwgi ni Jehova Nyasaye kaka ondiki e kitap Musa. Kamano bende e kaka negitimo kod dhok.
\v 13 Ne gibulo jamni mag Pasaka ewi mach kaka chik owacho to ring misengini maler ne gitedo e agulni gi pipni kod sufuriache kendo negipogo ji mapiyo piyo.
\v 14 Bangʼ mano negiloso mag-gi giwegi kod misango mag jodolo nikech jodolo mane gin Nyikwa Harun ne timo misengini miwangʼo pep kod misango mag boche nyaka otieno, omiyo jo-Lawi noloso mag-gi giwegi kod mag jodolo ma nyikwa Harun.
\p 
\v 15 Jower ma nyikwa Asaf ne nitiere keregi kaluwore gi chik mar Daudi gi mar Asaf gi mar Heman kod mar Jeduthun janen mar ruoth. Jorit dhorangeye ne ok owuok kuondegi mag rito nikech owetegi ma jo-Lawi nosetedonigi.
\p 
\v 16 Kamano tije Jehova Nyasaye duto mar Sap Pasaka kod mar timo misengini miwangʼo pep e kendo mar misango mar Jehova Nyasaye notim chiengʼono, kaka ruoth Josia nochiko.
\v 17 Jo-Israel duto mane nitiere nochamo Pasaka e ndalono kendo negitimo Sap Makati ma ok oketie Thowi kuom ndalo abiriyo.
\v 18 Pasaka machal kamano ne pok otim e Israel chakre ndalo mag Samuel janabi; kendo onge ruodh Israel moro amora ma nosetimo Pasaka machal gi mane Josia kaachiel gi jodolo, jo-Lawi kod jo-Juda duto gi jo-Israel mane oriwore gi jo-Jerusalem otimo.
\v 19 Pasakani notim e higa mar apar gaboro mar loch Josia.
\s1 Tho mar Josia
\p 
\v 20 Bangʼ kane Josia osetieko loso hekalu, Neko ruodh Misri nodhi mondo oked e dala mar Karkemish man but Yufrate mi Josia nodhi mondo orad kode e lweny.
\v 21 To Neko noorone joote mondo owachne niya, “En angʼo ma walaro kodi yaye ruodh Juda? In ok ema abiro amonji e kindeni, to amonjo dhoot ma wakedogo. Nyasaye osenyisa mondo atim piyo omiyo kik ipiem gi Nyasaye ma jakora ka ok kamano to obiro tieki.”
\p 
\v 22 Kata kamano, Josia ne ok oweye, omiyo nodhi korwakore magalagala mondo oked kode. Ne ok odewo gima Neko nonyise kaluwore gi gima Nyasaye ochiko to nodhi mokedo kode e paw Megido.
\p 
\v 23 Jodir asere nochielo ruoth Josia mi nowacho ni jotichne niya, “Golauru ka nimar asehinyora marach.”
\v 24 Omiyo ne gigole e gache ma gikete e gari machielo mane en-go ma gikele Jerusalem kama nothoe. Noyike e liete mag kwerene kendo jo-Juda kod jo-Jerusalem duto noywage.
\p 
\v 25 Jeremia nochwogo wend ywak ni Josia kendo jower duto machwo gi mamon pod wero wendno ka giparogo Josia nyaka chil kawuono. Gino oselokore tim jo-Israel kendo wendno ondik e kitap Ywagruok.
\p 
\v 26 Weche mag ndalo mamoko mag loch Josia kod tichne maber manotimo koluwore gi gima ondiki e Chik mar Jehova Nyasaye,
\v 27 gigo manotimo duto aa chakruokgi nyaka gikogi ondik e kitap ruodhi mag Israel kod Juda.
\c 36
\nb 
\v 1 Kendo jopinyno nokawo Jehoahaz wuod Josia mokete obedo ruoth e Jerusalem kar wuon mare.
\s1 Jehoahaz ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 2 Jehoahaz ne ja-higni piero ariyo gadek kane odoko ruoth kendo nobedo e loch kodak Jerusalem kuom dweche adek.
\v 3 Ruodh jo-Misri nogole e loch Jerusalem kendo nochuno jo-Juda mondo ochiw osuru mar fedha ma pekne romo kilo alufu adek gi mia angʼwen kod dhahabu ma pekne romo kilo piero adek gangʼwen.
\v 4 Ruodh Misri noketo Eliakim owadgi Jehoahaz ruodh Juda kod Jerusalem kendo noloko nying Eliakim ni Jehoyakim. Neko nokawo Jehoahaz owadgi Eliakim mi otero e twech Misri.
\s1 Jehoyakim ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 5 Jehoyakim ne ja-higni piero ariyo gabich kane odoko ruoth kendo nobedo e loch kuom higni apar gachiel kodak Jerusalem. Kendo notimo gik maricho e nyim wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache.
\v 6 Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon nomonje motweye gi rateke mag mula motere Babulon.
\v 7 Bende Nebukadneza nokawo gige lemo mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye moketogi e hekalu mare e piny Babulon.
\p 
\v 8 Kuom gik mamoko duto mag ndalo loch Jehoyakim, timbe maricho manotimo kod ketho malingʼ-lingʼ mane ofweny kuome, ondiki e kitap ruodhi mag Israel kod Juda. Kendo Jehoyakin wuode nobedo ruoth kare.
\s1 Jehoyakin ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 9 Jehoyakin ne ja-higni apar gaboro kane odoko ruoth kendo nobedo e loch kodak Jerusalem kuom dweche adek kod ndalo apar. Notimo richo e nyim wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 10 E ndalo chwiri ruoth Nebukadneza nooro wach mondo oome otere Babulon kaachiel gi gige lemo mabeyo mag hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kendo noketo owadgi wuon Jehoyakin, ma nyinge Zedekia mondo obed ruodh Juda kod Jerusalem.
\s1 Zedekia ruodh Juda
\p 
\v 11 Zedekia ne ja-higni piero ariyo gachiel kane obedo ruoth kendo nobedo e loch kuom higni apar gachiel kodak Jerusalem.
\v 12 Notimo richo e nyim Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache kendo ne ok obolore e nyim Jeremia janabi mane nyise wach Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 13 Bende nongʼanyo ni ruoth Nebukadneza mane okete mokwongʼore gi nying Nyasaye. Ne toke obedo matek ta kendo chunye ne ok odewo mondo oduog ir Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel.
\v 14 To bende jotelo madongo duto mag jodolo kod ji nomedo bedo joma ok jo-ratiro, ka giluwo timbe mamono mag oganda kendo ne gichido hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye mane osepwodho Jerusalem.
\s1 Podho mar Jerusalem
\p 
\v 15 Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach kweregi nooronegi wach kokalo kuom jootene kinde ka kinde nikech nokecho joge kod kar dakne.
\v 16 To negimedo jaro joote Nyasaye ka gichayo wechene kendo ka ginyiero jonabi mage nyaka mirima nomako Jehova Nyasaye kod joge maonge kaka dikony.
\v 17 Omiyo ne okelonigi ruodh jo-Babulon mane onego yawuotgi matindo gi ligangla e kama ler mar lemo kendo ne ok okecho wuowi kata nyako, ngʼat motegno kata jaduongʼ moti. Nyasaye nochiwogi duto e lwet Nebukadneza.
\v 18 Nokawo gige lemo duto madongo gi matindo mane nitiere e hekalu mar Nyasaye, kod gik mane okan e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye gi gik moko duto mane okan e od ruoth kod od jodonge moterogi Babulon.
\v 19 Ne giwangʼo hekalu mar Nyasaye kendo negimuko ohinga mar Jerusalem; mane giwangʼo ute ruoth duto kendo negiketho gimoro amora ma nengogi tek mane ni kanyo.
\p 
\v 20 Nokawo jogo mane otony e nek mag ligangla noterogi e twech Babulon kendo olokogi wasumbinige kod mag yawuote nyaka ochopo ndalo mane jo-Pasia okawe loch.
\v 21 Piny nobedo mamor koyudo yweyone mag Sabato, kinde duto mane odongʼ gunda, nyaka higni piero abiriyo orumo mana kaka wach Jehova Nyasaye nowacho gi dho Jeremia.
\p 
\v 22 E higa mokwongo mar loch Sairas ruodh Pasia, mondo ochop singo mar wach Jehova Nyasaye mane Jeremia okoro, Jehova Nyasaye nowuoyo gi chuny Sairas ruodh Pasia mondo ogol lendo e pinye duto koketo e ndiko kama:
\pmo 
\v 23 Ma e gima Sairas ruodh Pasia wacho:
\pm “ ‘Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach polo osemiya pinjeruodhi duto manie piny kendo oseyiera mondo agerne hekalu e Jerusalem manie piny Juda. Ngʼato angʼata kuom joge manie dieru, nyalo dhi kendo mad Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache bed kode.’ ”
